WEBVTT

1
00:00:06.000 --> 00:00:12.074
Watch Online Movies and Series for FREE
www.osdb.link/lm

2
00:01:24.208 --> 00:01:25.542
<i>Anni.</i> where's brother?

3
00:01:26.000 --> 00:01:27.280
- He's in the backyard.
- In class?

4
00:01:57.583 --> 00:01:58.583
One.

5
00:01:58.875 --> 00:01:59.875
two.

6
00:02:00.167 --> 00:02:01.167
three.

7
00:02:01.458 --> 00:02:02.458
four.

8
00:02:02.875 --> 00:02:03.875
five…

9
00:02:04.083 --> 00:02:04.958
- What?
- Brother.

10
00:02:05.042 --> 00:02:06.601
I'm going to Parry's Corner
to restock medicines.

11
00:02:06.625 --> 00:02:07.809
Can you watch the shop
until I get back?

12
00:02:07.833 --> 00:02:08.893
- Will do. Go ahead.
- Okay. brother.

13
00:02:08.917 --> 00:02:11.583
Also. we made a list of
the out-of-stock tablets. right?

14
00:02:12.000 --> 00:02:13.143
- Make sure nothing's missing.
- Okay.

15
00:02:13.167 --> 00:02:14.167
Go on.

16
00:02:17.167 --> 00:02:18.847
- Handle the class for a bit.
- Okay. Master.

17
00:02:21.667 --> 00:02:22.667
Mom…

18
00:02:23.417 --> 00:02:26.667
- Rohan from next door hit me!
- Nila!

19
00:02:28.833 --> 00:02:29.833
Who started it. dear?

20
00:02:30.042 --> 00:02:31.375
He did.

21
00:02:32.333 --> 00:02:33.494
Then what are your hands for?

22
00:02:35.417 --> 00:02:36.417
Hit him back!

23
00:02:42.708 --> 00:02:43.792
Hey. come on!

24
00:02:46.083 --> 00:02:47.083
Rohan!

25
00:02:52.958 --> 00:02:54.833
Oh. back for more already?

26
00:03:10.167 --> 00:03:12.250
Mom!

27
00:03:14.667 --> 00:03:15.667
Mom!

28
00:03:17.167 --> 00:03:20.000
Rohan kicked me. Mom!

29
00:03:21.958 --> 00:03:22.958
Nila.

30
00:03:26.750 --> 00:03:27.875
Let me see.

31
00:03:28.083 --> 00:03:29.208
Oh. my!

32
00:03:30.292 --> 00:03:31.292
Come here.

33
00:03:32.625 --> 00:03:33.875
Do you know something?

34
00:03:35.083 --> 00:03:36.167
It was Rohan today.

35
00:03:37.083 --> 00:03:39.364
It could be someone else tomorrow.
There'll be others too.

36
00:03:39.917 --> 00:03:41.000
They'll just keep coming.

37
00:03:41.833 --> 00:03:44.667
Mom and Dad won't
always be with you.

38
00:03:45.750 --> 00:03:47.430
You need to learn how to protect yourself.

39
00:03:50.042 --> 00:03:53.125
In that case.
I want to learn karate too.

40
00:03:54.542 --> 00:03:55.542
Really?

41
00:03:55.833 --> 00:03:56.833
Yes.

42
00:04:03.417 --> 00:04:07.542
<i>You tried to measure her beauty
But she's fire. burning bright.</i>

43
00:04:07.625 --> 00:04:12.083
<i>Who is she
Lighting up the sky like a star?</i>

44
00:04:12.583 --> 00:04:14.625
<i>Shut her behind doors.</i>

45
00:04:14.708 --> 00:04:16.958
<i>She'll break them all
Rising like a fire.</i>

46
00:04:17.042 --> 00:04:18.917
<i>- Who is she?</i>
- Nila!

47
00:04:19.000 --> 00:04:21.333
<i>- Watch her action!</i>
- Wow! A teddy!

48
00:04:21.792 --> 00:04:26.417
<i>Her eyes cut deep like waves in motion.</i>

49
00:04:26.500 --> 00:04:28.458
<i>You're all dead!</i>

50
00:04:28.542 --> 00:04:30.708
<i>Stand as her opponent
One strike will end the fight.</i>

51
00:04:30.792 --> 00:04:34.250
<i>She walks in strong among the many.</i>

52
00:04:35.250 --> 00:04:39.125
<i>Watch her win a thousand times
Just watch.</i>

53
00:04:39.750 --> 00:04:43.583
<i>She's the face
Of strength and splendor.</i>

54
00:04:44.292 --> 00:04:48.375
<i>She's got no limits
She stands a queen tonight.</i>

55
00:04:57.833 --> 00:04:58.833
Rohan!

56
00:05:02.625 --> 00:05:03.625
What?

57
00:05:27.667 --> 00:05:28.667
Nila.

58
00:05:28.917 --> 00:05:31.167
if it breaks.
how will we watch TV?

59
00:05:31.250 --> 00:05:32.531
Be gentle with the remote. okay?

60
00:05:33.375 --> 00:05:34.375
Uncle.

61
00:05:35.125 --> 00:05:36.708
What's that medicine for?

62
00:05:36.792 --> 00:05:38.833
- That's for cough.
- What about that?

63
00:05:39.458 --> 00:05:41.250
- It's a tonic for stomach aches.
- Oh.

64
00:05:41.542 --> 00:05:43.375
- And this?
- Which...

65
00:05:44.750 --> 00:05:45.750
To make people cough.

66
00:05:46.250 --> 00:05:47.250
It's mine.

67
00:05:47.958 --> 00:05:48.958
so don't tell your dad.

68
00:05:51.375 --> 00:05:53.583
Look how badly she beat my son.

69
00:05:58.000 --> 00:06:01.083
You're only supposed to fight
during a match. not outside.

70
00:06:01.167 --> 00:06:02.167
Got it?

71
00:06:02.750 --> 00:06:06.750
No one should mess with you
just because you're a girl.

72
00:06:07.208 --> 00:06:08.208
Okay?

73
00:06:08.958 --> 00:06:11.708
She hit him again for snitching on her.

74
00:06:12.625 --> 00:06:16.833
<i>Times will change
And break your pride down.</i>

75
00:06:17.333 --> 00:06:21.375
<i>Stopping her is stopping yourself.</i>

76
00:06:21.958 --> 00:06:26.500
<i>She's a hero. feel her power.</i>

77
00:06:26.583 --> 00:06:31.250
<i>In her rise. you fade to zero.</i>

78
00:06:34.125 --> 00:06:35.917
How many times should I call you?

79
00:06:36.125 --> 00:06:37.583
Come out and eat now!

80
00:06:39.417 --> 00:06:41.000
What's my darling doing?

81
00:06:41.917 --> 00:06:43.000
Had dinner?

82
00:06:44.333 --> 00:06:46.833
- Can't sleep?
- Yes. I can't.

83
00:06:46.958 --> 00:06:48.667
I lost the match.

84
00:06:50.292 --> 00:06:51.458
But this is your last time.

85
00:06:51.708 --> 00:06:53.000
You won't lose again.

86
00:06:53.083 --> 00:06:55.000
- You'll see for yourself.
- How?

87
00:06:55.375 --> 00:06:56.375
I'll tell you.

88
00:06:56.458 --> 00:06:59.875
I've competed in 34 tournaments so far.

89
00:06:59.958 --> 00:07:01.417
I lost only one.

90
00:07:02.292 --> 00:07:03.333
That night.

91
00:07:03.667 --> 00:07:04.833
I couldn't sleep.

92
00:07:05.417 --> 00:07:07.167
I couldn't stop thinking about it.

93
00:07:07.500 --> 00:07:08.958
It drove me crazy.

94
00:07:09.625 --> 00:07:10.625
It wasn't the loss.

95
00:07:11.125 --> 00:07:15.250
It was the need to never relive that night
that drove me to fight.

96
00:07:16.375 --> 00:07:18.375
After that. I never lost again.

97
00:07:20.125 --> 00:07:21.375
You're just like me. aren't you?

98
00:07:22.542 --> 00:07:25.083
From now on. you'll only win.

99
00:07:26.417 --> 00:07:30.458
<i>She walks in strong among the many.</i>

100
00:07:31.167 --> 00:07:35.208
<i>Watch her win a thousand times
Just watch.</i>

101
00:07:35.833 --> 00:07:39.667
<i>She's the face
Of strength and splendor.</i>

102
00:07:40.375 --> 00:07:44.167
<i>She's got no limits
She stands a queen tonight.</i>

103
00:08:10.125 --> 00:08:11.167
Uncle…

104
00:08:12.333 --> 00:08:14.417
Dad taught me karate.

105
00:08:15.292 --> 00:08:17.958
So who taught him?

106
00:08:18.042 --> 00:08:19.042
Your grandpa.

107
00:08:19.750 --> 00:08:21.125
Dad's dad?

108
00:08:21.875 --> 00:08:23.417
Your mother's dad.

109
00:08:29.500 --> 00:08:35.458
Out of 34 tournaments.
he said he lost only one. right?

110
00:08:42.375 --> 00:08:43.375
Yeah.

111
00:08:43.458 --> 00:08:45.875
Do you know who beat him?

112
00:08:57.000 --> 00:08:58.208
Your mother.

113
00:08:58.500 --> 00:08:59.667
My mother?!

114
00:09:15.208 --> 00:09:16.750
HOTEL BALAMURUGAN.

115
00:09:17.125 --> 00:09:18.292
What do you guys want?

116
00:09:18.625 --> 00:09:19.875
Ask them what they've got.

117
00:09:20.250 --> 00:09:21.250
Hey.

118
00:09:22.167 --> 00:09:24.458
- Pack some extra <i>sambar.</i>
- Okay.

119
00:09:25.542 --> 00:09:28.750
Remember Bhaskar? He tipped off
the cops about our bootlegging spot.

120
00:09:29.042 --> 00:09:30.042
That's his son. right?

121
00:09:30.375 --> 00:09:32.333
- That's him!
- Son!

122
00:09:33.750 --> 00:09:34.750
Come here.

123
00:09:36.125 --> 00:09:37.125
Tell me. bro?

124
00:09:43.125 --> 00:09:44.934
His dad will be terrified seeing
his son come home covered in blood.

125
00:09:44.958 --> 00:09:46.833
Punch him hard in the face!

126
00:09:48.042 --> 00:09:49.750
Bro. please.
Let me go. bro.

127
00:09:50.042 --> 00:09:51.167
Brother…

128
00:09:54.125 --> 00:09:55.750
Oh look. the hero's here!

129
00:10:00.500 --> 00:10:02.042
Hey. stop pinching me. man.

130
00:10:02.167 --> 00:10:03.167
Just let it go.

131
00:10:05.917 --> 00:10:07.208
It hurts!

132
00:10:07.625 --> 00:10:09.417
Oh. God! It hurts!

133
00:10:10.792 --> 00:10:12.292
Hey. let go of my hand.

134
00:10:13.583 --> 00:10:16.125
- Let go. man!
- I'll let go only if the boy tells me to.

135
00:10:16.208 --> 00:10:17.208
My hand!

136
00:10:19.667 --> 00:10:20.667
Let go. man!

137
00:10:23.042 --> 00:10:24.042
Let it go!

138
00:10:34.750 --> 00:10:36.000
Let go!

139
00:10:55.708 --> 00:10:57.583
I'll never cross you.
Tell him to let go. son.

140
00:10:57.667 --> 00:10:59.833
It hurts. man.
Please tell him to let go.

141
00:11:00.125 --> 00:11:01.226
Poor guy.
Let him go. brother.

142
00:11:01.250 --> 00:11:02.625
It hurts. man!

143
00:11:24.625 --> 00:11:25.625
Superb!

144
00:11:41.292 --> 00:11:43.917
Dad. do you know that boy
from the hotel?

145
00:11:44.583 --> 00:11:45.583
No. dear.

146
00:11:47.708 --> 00:11:50.083
Then why did you
fight for him. Dad?

147
00:11:53.167 --> 00:11:54.167
Nila…

148
00:11:55.542 --> 00:11:56.875
I had a younger sister.

149
00:11:57.375 --> 00:11:59.167
I was about ten then.

150
00:11:59.583 --> 00:12:01.167
I adored her.

151
00:12:01.542 --> 00:12:03.042
Something terrible
happened to her.

152
00:12:04.208 --> 00:12:05.750
People just stood there.

153
00:12:06.292 --> 00:12:08.375
saying nothing.

154
00:12:08.750 --> 00:12:10.458
If even one person had spoken up.

155
00:12:10.917 --> 00:12:14.083
my sister would still be with us today.

156
00:12:14.625 --> 00:12:16.375
Her name was Nila.

157
00:12:17.417 --> 00:12:18.458
You were named after her.

158
00:12:26.417 --> 00:12:27.417
Nila…

159
00:12:28.333 --> 00:12:33.708
If something happened to your mom
or me right in front of you.

160
00:12:34.042 --> 00:12:35.042
what would you do?

161
00:12:35.625 --> 00:12:36.750
I won't let it slide.

162
00:12:38.125 --> 00:12:39.125
Good.

163
00:12:39.333 --> 00:12:40.333
But

164
00:12:40.583 --> 00:12:44.125
you don't have to know the victim
to stand up for them.

165
00:12:44.833 --> 00:12:46.625
Every injustice must be confronted!

166
00:12:47.042 --> 00:12:50.000
That's when our lives gain meaning.

167
00:13:17.417 --> 00:13:22.000
My wife said you waited a long time
before leaving.

168
00:13:22.292 --> 00:13:24.083
I just came home.
Tell me. ma'am.

169
00:13:24.542 --> 00:13:28.917
Sir. my husband drove a cycle rickshaw.
saved every little bit.

170
00:13:29.083 --> 00:13:31.333
and bought that land
near the rickshaw stand.

171
00:13:31.500 --> 00:13:32.875
Before he passed.

172
00:13:32.958 --> 00:13:36.292
<i>he told me to sell the land
for our daughter's wedding.</i>

173
00:13:36.417 --> 00:13:37.583
<i>After his death.</i>

174
00:13:37.875 --> 00:13:43.042
Sundaram's men forged the papers
and claimed the land as theirs.

175
00:13:43.125 --> 00:13:46.583
They are threatening
to kill my daughter

176
00:13:46.667 --> 00:13:48.750
if I don't give them the
original documents tonight.

177
00:13:49.125 --> 00:13:51.833
<i>I'm heading to their place
with the original documents.</i>

178
00:13:51.917 --> 00:13:53.875
Can you please talk to them?

179
00:13:54.500 --> 00:13:59.042
I'm scared they'll hurt my daughter
if I go to the police.

180
00:13:59.500 --> 00:14:00.500
Ma'am.

181
00:14:00.583 --> 00:14:01.583
I understand your pain.

182
00:14:01.958 --> 00:14:03.458
But they are Sundaram's men.

183
00:14:03.542 --> 00:14:07.292
If it were someone else.
I could've helped you.

184
00:14:07.375 --> 00:14:10.833
They just want the documents
to leave you alone. right?

185
00:14:11.125 --> 00:14:13.143
Just give it to them.
and consider them gone for good.

186
00:14:13.167 --> 00:14:14.792
<i>They are ruthless monsters.</i>

187
00:14:18.000 --> 00:14:21.042
Sundaram promised me ten percent
if this land issue is solved.

188
00:14:21.250 --> 00:14:23.917
And this old lady wants me
to talk for her!

189
00:14:24.125 --> 00:14:25.125
Pathetic!

190
00:14:52.458 --> 00:14:53.819
Those for Purasaiwakkam. get down.

191
00:15:11.000 --> 00:15:12.375
Check who's out there!

192
00:15:13.750 --> 00:15:14.750
Move!

193
00:15:18.250 --> 00:15:19.375
No one's there. bro.

194
00:15:20.833 --> 00:15:22.417
Hey. who hit you. man?

195
00:15:32.083 --> 00:15:33.083
Me?

196
00:17:14.417 --> 00:17:16.292
Where are the forged land papers?

197
00:17:17.417 --> 00:17:19.208
Hey. bring those documents. man.

198
00:17:28.500 --> 00:17:29.500
Ask him to tear it.

199
00:17:29.917 --> 00:17:30.917
Do it. man.

200
00:17:33.875 --> 00:17:38.000
Don't you dare target the helpless.
thinking they have no one.

201
00:17:38.958 --> 00:17:40.292
If you do. remember this pain.

202
00:17:48.583 --> 00:17:49.750
Go home. ma'am.

203
00:17:49.917 --> 00:17:51.917
They won't mess with you again.

204
00:17:52.250 --> 00:17:53.958
You did this for me?

205
00:17:54.208 --> 00:17:56.042
Do you know me?

206
00:18:29.417 --> 00:18:31.833
HORRIFIC FACTORY ACCIDENT
47 WORKERS KILLED IN BLAZE

207
00:18:31.917 --> 00:18:34.708
In the explosion
at the Saadhuri chemical factory.

208
00:18:34.833 --> 00:18:36.625
<i>47 workers lost their lives.</i>

209
00:18:36.833 --> 00:18:42.000
The government has declared
the premises unfit for habitation.

210
00:18:42.167 --> 00:18:45.250
<i>I found out that
this was a planned accident.</i>

211
00:18:45.333 --> 00:18:48.417
A private mineral company has now

212
00:18:48.500 --> 00:18:52.917
leased the land for a coal mining project.

213
00:18:53.042 --> 00:18:55.458
<i>The company behind this incident is.</i>

214
00:18:55.875 --> 00:18:57.917
<i>Textas Minerals Private Limited.</i>

215
00:18:58.208 --> 00:18:59.208
<i>There's more.</i>

216
00:18:59.458 --> 00:19:01.792
<i>In Tamil Nadu. most of the projects</i>

217
00:19:02.167 --> 00:19:05.000
<i>undertaken by Textas Minerals Company
over the last five years</i>

218
00:19:05.083 --> 00:19:06.583
<i>have had similar incidents.</i>

219
00:19:06.750 --> 00:19:10.042
<i>All these incidents cannot be accidents.</i>

220
00:19:10.333 --> 00:19:12.125
<i>I figured out that</i>

221
00:19:12.333 --> 00:19:17.458
<i>if they wanted a place for mining.
they would do anything to get it.</i>

222
00:19:17.833 --> 00:19:20.417
Everyone's plots are being traded.

223
00:19:37.667 --> 00:19:39.667
An entire village has vanished!

224
00:19:43.708 --> 00:19:46.167
What's the secret behind
the death of 1.000 elephants?

225
00:19:46.250 --> 00:19:47.930
WHAT CAUSED THE DEATHS OF 1.000 ELEPHANTS?

226
00:19:51.167 --> 00:19:54.500
<i>There's one man behind
this heartless group of killers.</i>

227
00:20:09.875 --> 00:20:11.000
<i>Varun Dayalan.</i>

228
00:20:22.708 --> 00:20:24.417
<i>The company's next target…</i>

229
00:20:26.708 --> 00:20:29.750
So far. we've mined
thousands of stones and diamonds in India.

230
00:20:29.833 --> 00:20:31.750
But this Black Opal
is far more valuable.

231
00:20:32.500 --> 00:20:35.000
There's a huge demand for this
in the world market.

232
00:20:35.792 --> 00:20:38.792
Here. in Keelakadu village.
1.500 feet below this location.

233
00:20:39.042 --> 00:20:43.500
our research team has found
a huge Black Opal rock.

234
00:20:43.708 --> 00:20:46.583
It's about 150 feet long
and 130 feet wide.

235
00:20:46.833 --> 00:20:49.917
Its current market worth
is more than 70 billion.

236
00:20:54.167 --> 00:20:55.167
<i>Keelakadu.</i>

237
00:20:55.583 --> 00:20:57.000
<i>Approximately 800 families.</i>

238
00:20:57.417 --> 00:21:00.167
<i>It's a small tribal village.
home to families for generations.</i>

239
00:21:00.458 --> 00:21:03.083
<i>Farming is the only occupation they know.</i>

240
00:21:03.500 --> 00:21:07.167
<i>Their hills and forests are their Gods.
They are everything to them.</i>

241
00:21:08.042 --> 00:21:11.125
<i>I found out that.
for the last five years.</i>

242
00:21:11.333 --> 00:21:15.583
<i>Varun Dayalan's research team
has been searching for a very rare mineral</i>

243
00:21:15.792 --> 00:21:17.042
<i>in those hills.</i>

244
00:21:17.500 --> 00:21:21.083
Even if we get the permission to mine.
we've got two problems to face.

245
00:21:21.458 --> 00:21:22.458
What are they?

246
00:21:22.625 --> 00:21:24.708
When we drill below 1.500 feet.

247
00:21:24.792 --> 00:21:27.875
the pressure and vibration
will cause a huge landslide.

248
00:21:28.375 --> 00:21:31.708
The entire Keelakadu village
will get submerged in that avalanche.

249
00:21:31.917 --> 00:21:35.500
More than 1.300 people might die.

250
00:21:35.625 --> 00:21:38.708
So. the government will not
grant us permission to mine the place.

251
00:21:38.833 --> 00:21:40.667
And our second threat is Karthikeyan.

252
00:21:41.792 --> 00:21:43.250
He's a social environmentalist.

253
00:21:43.833 --> 00:21:47.875
We've got intel that
he's analyzing all our projects.

254
00:21:48.500 --> 00:21:51.042
He's collecting data about all our
previous projects

255
00:21:51.125 --> 00:21:52.208
from various sources. sir.

256
00:21:52.917 --> 00:21:54.157
So. we have to handle him. too.

257
00:21:54.500 --> 00:21:55.875
to start our next project. sir.

258
00:22:05.333 --> 00:22:06.958
Mom. I'm getting late!

259
00:22:15.083 --> 00:22:17.250
Dear. do you know something?

260
00:22:17.792 --> 00:22:20.417
Women might
love their husbands a lot.

261
00:22:20.667 --> 00:22:23.792
But after having a child.
half their love shifts to the child.

262
00:22:24.125 --> 00:22:28.875
For men. love for their wives
grows tenfold after a child.

263
00:22:29.125 --> 00:22:31.250
Why are you blabbering now?

264
00:22:31.583 --> 00:22:33.292
You got the first <i>dosa.</i>

265
00:22:33.458 --> 00:22:35.333
That's why he's lamenting now.

266
00:22:35.417 --> 00:22:36.750
But your mom's different.

267
00:22:38.208 --> 00:22:39.208
She's special!

268
00:22:40.792 --> 00:22:42.750
First day of work?

269
00:22:42.875 --> 00:22:44.167
- Yes. Uncle.
- Alright.

270
00:22:44.292 --> 00:22:45.692
- Had breakfast?
- I'll have it later.

271
00:22:46.792 --> 00:22:48.072
Your office is in Egmore. right?

272
00:22:48.417 --> 00:22:49.833
How are you planning to travel?

273
00:22:50.125 --> 00:22:51.375
The cab will pick me up. Uncle.

274
00:22:51.458 --> 00:22:53.250
Okay. okay. Be careful.

275
00:23:01.500 --> 00:23:02.500
Hello. sir.

276
00:23:02.625 --> 00:23:03.542
- Hello.
- New recruit.

277
00:23:03.625 --> 00:23:04.708
Nila? Okay.

278
00:23:09.583 --> 00:23:10.458
Rakesh.

279
00:23:10.583 --> 00:23:11.583
Sir?

280
00:23:12.083 --> 00:23:13.083
She's a fresher.

281
00:23:13.167 --> 00:23:14.958
<i>Explain the entire procedure to her.</i>

282
00:23:17.292 --> 00:23:19.958
Why isn't patient Krishnakumar's
account closed yet?

283
00:23:20.292 --> 00:23:22.092
<i>We're processing.
We'll credit it in two days.</i>

284
00:23:22.167 --> 00:23:23.167
Thank you.

285
00:23:37.208 --> 00:23:38.208
Breathe!

286
00:23:48.792 --> 00:23:49.792
Three!

287
00:23:50.333 --> 00:23:51.333
Four!

288
00:23:53.833 --> 00:23:55.167
Change the TV. Uncle.

289
00:23:55.750 --> 00:23:57.500
I'm getting a headache
from all these lines.

290
00:23:58.708 --> 00:23:59.958
We just changed the fridge.

291
00:24:00.292 --> 00:24:01.875
There's no hurry.
We'll change it later.

292
00:24:02.917 --> 00:24:04.208
The business is good. right?

293
00:24:04.292 --> 00:24:05.601
What are you going to do
with all the money?

294
00:24:05.625 --> 00:24:06.667
About that…

295
00:24:07.042 --> 00:24:08.042
I'll buy a house…

296
00:24:08.625 --> 00:24:09.667
I'll shift there.

297
00:24:10.458 --> 00:24:13.583
I'll escape from your nagging.
That's why I'm saving up.

298
00:24:14.667 --> 00:24:15.958
Great idea. Uncle.

299
00:24:16.417 --> 00:24:17.917
Invite me to the housewarming.

300
00:24:18.167 --> 00:24:19.167
I'll smack you.

301
00:24:19.333 --> 00:24:22.000
This TV's good for the next ten years.
Just don't break the remote.

302
00:24:45.750 --> 00:24:47.893
It'd have been easier
if we had drained the water earlier.

303
00:24:47.917 --> 00:24:49.375
- Just be careful.
- Sure. sir.

304
00:24:50.208 --> 00:24:51.208
Bro.

305
00:24:51.250 --> 00:24:52.583
will a single bathroom do?

306
00:24:52.958 --> 00:24:53.958
That'll do.

307
00:24:54.208 --> 00:24:55.667
We've got two bathrooms inside.

308
00:24:55.833 --> 00:24:57.208
More students have joined.

309
00:24:57.542 --> 00:24:59.167
That's why I'm building one here.

310
00:24:59.333 --> 00:25:00.333
Okay. brother.

311
00:25:00.458 --> 00:25:03.375
Tell us if you've got
something else to be fixed.

312
00:25:03.542 --> 00:25:04.417
We'll get it done.

313
00:25:04.500 --> 00:25:05.750
- For sure.
- Thanks. bro.

314
00:25:12.458 --> 00:25:13.458
<i>Yes. sir?</i>

315
00:25:13.500 --> 00:25:15.667
Some idiot broke
into the go down and ran off

316
00:25:15.750 --> 00:25:17.059
with the seized half kilo of marijuana.

317
00:25:17.083 --> 00:25:20.500
<i>If the inspector learns about this.</i>

318
00:25:21.000 --> 00:25:22.000
I'm dead.

319
00:25:22.542 --> 00:25:25.102
I have to produce the seized material
in court on Monday morning.

320
00:25:25.625 --> 00:25:26.875
Can you do something?

321
00:25:27.292 --> 00:25:29.792
Sir. it'll take two days
for me to arrange something.

322
00:25:30.083 --> 00:25:32.083
Pandi. you know very well.

323
00:25:32.542 --> 00:25:33.958
I've done so much for you.

324
00:25:34.250 --> 00:25:36.167
Sir. I said I don't have the stuff.

325
00:25:36.250 --> 00:25:37.651
<i>I never said I couldn't arrange it.</i>

326
00:25:38.500 --> 00:25:40.792
A guy's brought some stuff
into Ayanavaram.

327
00:25:41.292 --> 00:25:42.625
<i>Tell him that I sent you.</i>

328
00:25:42.917 --> 00:25:43.957
He'll definitely help you.

329
00:25:44.708 --> 00:25:46.548
Alright. Give me his details.
I'll talk to him.

330
00:25:46.708 --> 00:25:48.029
<i>- Reached the station?</i>
- Yeah. dear.

331
00:25:48.125 --> 00:25:49.926
I came straight to the station
from the court.

332
00:25:50.292 --> 00:25:51.559
I'll finish my duty.
and I'll be home tomorrow morning.

333
00:25:51.583 --> 00:25:53.292
- I'll call you later.
- Alright.

334
00:25:53.458 --> 00:25:55.042
- Dear. hang on a minute.
<i>- What is it?</i>

335
00:25:55.125 --> 00:25:57.417
It's Harish's PTM tomorrow.

336
00:25:57.750 --> 00:26:01.625
Don't hurt him again as you did
on Sports Day by not coming.

337
00:26:02.083 --> 00:26:03.583
We are going together tomorrow.

338
00:26:05.375 --> 00:26:06.583
- Okay?
- Okay.

339
00:26:11.667 --> 00:26:12.667
Sir.

340
00:26:12.958 --> 00:26:13.958
- Hello. sir.
- Sir.

341
00:26:14.833 --> 00:26:16.958
Sir. based on the complaint we received.

342
00:26:17.042 --> 00:26:20.000
we've got the guy who broke in
and harassed a girl in Shenoy Nagar.

343
00:26:22.625 --> 00:26:23.946
Should we put him in a cast. sir?

344
00:26:25.250 --> 00:26:27.208
It's you?

345
00:26:27.417 --> 00:26:31.292
When a girl adjusts her dress
even if we just turn her way.

346
00:26:31.708 --> 00:26:36.458
we start worrying
if she thinks we're creeps.

347
00:26:37.125 --> 00:26:40.458
But how can you guys do this
without an ounce of shame?

348
00:26:41.292 --> 00:26:42.208
Saami.

349
00:26:42.292 --> 00:26:43.750
- Hold his hand.
- Sir… please.

350
00:26:43.833 --> 00:26:46.375
- Please. sir. Please!
- Quit resisting!

351
00:26:47.250 --> 00:26:48.667
Sir. sir…
Oh. God!

352
00:26:48.750 --> 00:26:50.230
Sir. please let me go. sir.
I beg you.

353
00:26:52.000 --> 00:26:53.000
How dare you touch women?

354
00:26:53.375 --> 00:26:54.375
I'll show you.

355
00:26:54.417 --> 00:26:56.542
Sir. please don't.
I beg you. sir.

356
00:26:56.750 --> 00:26:57.851
- Sir. I won't do it again.
- Hold his hand.

357
00:26:57.875 --> 00:26:59.292
I won't do it again. sir.
I swear...

358
00:27:01.458 --> 00:27:02.458
Sir!

359
00:27:02.750 --> 00:27:05.333
Sir. please! Let me go!
Don't do this. sir!

360
00:27:17.667 --> 00:27:18.667
Hey!

361
00:27:19.167 --> 00:27:20.207
The food is bland as hell!

362
00:27:21.833 --> 00:27:23.809
How many times should I ask you
to add salt while cooking?

363
00:27:23.833 --> 00:27:25.875
It's just there.
Can't you add it yourself?

364
00:27:25.958 --> 00:27:28.417
I'm asking you to cook properly.
and you want me to add it?

365
00:27:29.958 --> 00:27:31.292
He's starting it again.

366
00:27:31.500 --> 00:27:32.500
Hey!

367
00:27:32.792 --> 00:27:33.792
I asked you to come here.

368
00:27:35.458 --> 00:27:36.625
Why do you keep shouting?

369
00:27:36.708 --> 00:27:37.708
I keep shouting?

370
00:27:37.875 --> 00:27:38.875
Hey!

371
00:27:39.208 --> 00:27:40.249
What the hell did you say?

372
00:27:41.583 --> 00:27:42.583
I keep shouting?

373
00:27:47.625 --> 00:27:48.500
Hit me.

374
00:27:48.583 --> 00:27:49.458
Hit me harder.

375
00:27:49.542 --> 00:27:50.417
Just kill me.

376
00:27:50.500 --> 00:27:52.500
You want me to add the salt?

377
00:27:53.417 --> 00:27:55.333
You've become brazen enough
to talk back to me?

378
00:27:55.708 --> 00:27:57.628
You didn't see me for a day.
and you grew bolder?

379
00:27:57.708 --> 00:27:58.583
What?

380
00:27:58.667 --> 00:27:59.667
I grew bolder?!

381
00:27:59.958 --> 00:28:01.958
Right. Talk more.

382
00:28:02.292 --> 00:28:04.172
You got arrested and sat
comfortably behind bars

383
00:28:04.583 --> 00:28:06.667
while my kids and I were
fighting for our lives.

384
00:28:06.833 --> 00:28:08.794
Now you're complaining about
the salt in the food?

385
00:28:10.000 --> 00:28:12.167
We haven't paid rent
in six months. Do you know that?

386
00:28:12.750 --> 00:28:14.625
Do you even have the means
to pay the rent?

387
00:28:14.958 --> 00:28:17.292
Hey. I'm warning you.

388
00:28:17.417 --> 00:28:18.958
Warning me?
For what?

389
00:28:19.125 --> 00:28:21.708
The landlord will show up tomorrow
and humiliate us.

390
00:28:22.042 --> 00:28:26.083
Be a man. Pay him first.
then yell at me.

391
00:28:27.792 --> 00:28:29.375
You can't even take care
of your family.

392
00:28:29.667 --> 00:28:31.292
And you want salt in your food?

393
00:29:02.375 --> 00:29:03.375
Hello?

394
00:29:03.667 --> 00:29:05.583
How long will you take
to attend a call?

395
00:29:05.667 --> 00:29:07.250
Why are you pissed now?

396
00:29:07.458 --> 00:29:08.458
What happened?

397
00:29:08.667 --> 00:29:09.667
I'm pissed?!

398
00:29:09.958 --> 00:29:11.958
<i>Apparently. I can touch her
only if I earn money.</i>

399
00:29:12.458 --> 00:29:14.500
I'll bring the money
and show her who I am.

400
00:29:15.375 --> 00:29:16.375
Yes. man.

401
00:29:16.417 --> 00:29:18.393
These women respect us
only if we show them the money.

402
00:29:18.417 --> 00:29:20.333
<i>Forget it. man.
Our good days are coming soon.</i>

403
00:29:21.292 --> 00:29:22.458
- Hey…
<i>- Yeah?</i>

404
00:29:23.042 --> 00:29:24.393
You said you'd get me
into Kirubakaran's gang.

405
00:29:24.417 --> 00:29:25.417
Did you talk to him?

406
00:29:25.542 --> 00:29:26.542
Hey…

407
00:29:26.667 --> 00:29:28.375
I had a word with him yesterday.

408
00:29:28.458 --> 00:29:29.542
He wanted to see you.

409
00:29:29.625 --> 00:29:31.208
I'll call you when I go there.

410
00:29:31.292 --> 00:29:32.625
Come with me. Alright?

411
00:29:41.000 --> 00:29:42.000
Nila?

412
00:29:42.042 --> 00:29:43.917
They've asked you
to use the system over there.

413
00:29:44.833 --> 00:29:46.417
Why? What's wrong with this one?

414
00:29:46.500 --> 00:29:49.000
I don't know.
The TL asked you to use that one.

415
00:29:49.125 --> 00:29:50.125
Come on.

416
00:29:50.292 --> 00:29:51.667
Oh… Okay.

417
00:29:52.250 --> 00:29:53.250
Kayal.

418
00:29:53.875 --> 00:29:56.083
Sir asked you
to use Nila's system.

419
00:30:26.208 --> 00:30:28.125
We can't clear those people
from there.

420
00:30:28.750 --> 00:30:30.125
They will not listen.

421
00:30:30.500 --> 00:30:33.292
They'll protest to stop the mining.

422
00:30:33.583 --> 00:30:37.542
If it reaches that stage.
I won't be able to help you.

423
00:30:37.625 --> 00:30:40.625
So it's better to keep this a secret.

424
00:30:41.375 --> 00:30:42.875
How many feet did you say?

425
00:30:43.583 --> 00:30:44.624
One thousand five hundred.

426
00:30:44.708 --> 00:30:50.208
I can grant you permission
to mine up to 300 feet without issue.

427
00:30:50.458 --> 00:30:52.417
So. I'll give you approval for 300 feet.

428
00:30:52.667 --> 00:30:54.625
You can dig as deep as you like.

429
00:30:55.458 --> 00:30:57.167
Even if the village gets destroyed.

430
00:30:57.750 --> 00:31:00.208
I'll make sure your company stays
out of that mess.

431
00:31:00.917 --> 00:31:02.708
So. how much is the project value?

432
00:31:03.417 --> 00:31:04.417
Seventy billion. sir.

433
00:31:06.250 --> 00:31:07.458
Seventy billion?!

434
00:31:08.917 --> 00:31:14.292
Transfer 15 percent. ten billion.
into my trust as legitimate funds.

435
00:31:14.875 --> 00:31:15.958
Ten billion?!

436
00:31:16.208 --> 00:31:19.542
You won't even give
ten billion for 1.300 lives?

437
00:31:20.083 --> 00:31:21.524
Also. this is a very risky business.

438
00:31:23.500 --> 00:31:25.458
Even if I get caught in the future.

439
00:31:26.500 --> 00:31:28.340
the sum should make up for it.
Don't you think?

440
00:31:41.000 --> 00:31:42.333
Call our accountant. Girish.

441
00:31:43.167 --> 00:31:44.167
Excuse me. sir.

442
00:31:44.667 --> 00:31:45.750
-Girish.
-Sir.

443
00:31:45.833 --> 00:31:47.643
How much money do we have
in our company account?

444
00:31:47.667 --> 00:31:49.187
Give me a second. sir.
I'll check that.

445
00:31:52.417 --> 00:31:54.292
Sir. 7.26 billion.

446
00:31:55.417 --> 00:31:57.083
Sell all our main shares.

447
00:31:57.542 --> 00:31:58.833
Take out all our black money.

448
00:31:59.208 --> 00:32:01.042
- We need to close this deal.
- Okay. sir.

449
00:32:09.542 --> 00:32:10.917
I want to talk to Abraham.

450
00:32:11.542 --> 00:32:12.542
Call him.

451
00:32:22.833 --> 00:32:23.708
Hello?

452
00:32:23.833 --> 00:32:26.333
Move ten billion into a trust account
as legitimate funds.

453
00:32:26.958 --> 00:32:29.292
This money is for a very important deal.

454
00:32:29.458 --> 00:32:32.833
I can't think of anyone better
to handle this.

455
00:32:33.250 --> 00:32:34.417
That's why I called you.

456
00:32:36.500 --> 00:32:37.500
It'll be done.

457
00:32:44.500 --> 00:32:46.083
I want to talk to Kirubakaran.

458
00:32:47.167 --> 00:32:48.792
I got rid of the bodies. bro.

459
00:32:49.042 --> 00:32:50.442
The police won't find any evidence.

460
00:32:50.583 --> 00:32:51.625
There's no problem here.

461
00:32:56.875 --> 00:32:58.755
- Yes. Varun?
- Someone needs to be taken care of.

462
00:32:59.333 --> 00:33:00.542
This is important.

463
00:33:01.292 --> 00:33:04.750
That's why I'm calling you
instead of giving it to my guys.

464
00:33:05.292 --> 00:33:08.125
<i>There's this social environmentalist.
Name's Karthikeyan.</i>

465
00:33:08.500 --> 00:33:10.708
I'll send you his details.

466
00:33:11.458 --> 00:33:12.458
Okay.

467
00:33:17.000 --> 00:33:18.000
Where's my brother?

468
00:33:18.042 --> 00:33:19.042
He's inside.

469
00:33:22.000 --> 00:33:23.040
Brother. you asked for me?

470
00:33:25.917 --> 00:33:26.917
Varun called.

471
00:33:27.250 --> 00:33:28.542
He wants someone gone.

472
00:33:29.750 --> 00:33:30.958
Mani has the details.

473
00:33:31.583 --> 00:33:33.500
- Get it done.
- I'll do it. bro. See you.

474
00:33:55.208 --> 00:33:59.958
<i>If I walk with pain
Knowing roads may burn</i>

475
00:34:00.250 --> 00:34:04.625
<i>I won't turn around.</i>

476
00:34:04.750 --> 00:34:09.542
<i>If my heart breaks now
Just to heal someday.</i>

477
00:34:09.833 --> 00:34:14.000
<i>That pain feels profound</i>

478
00:34:15.500 --> 00:34:17.792
Diya. tomorrow's my birthday.

479
00:34:17.917 --> 00:34:19.875
I'm cutting my birthday cake
in the evening.

480
00:34:19.958 --> 00:34:22.292
My mom asked me
to invite my friends.

481
00:34:22.417 --> 00:34:24.208
- Will you come over?
- Sure. I'll come.

482
00:34:24.292 --> 00:34:25.292
And you?

483
00:34:25.958 --> 00:34:27.417
Will you please come?

484
00:34:34.417 --> 00:34:41.375
<i>Whatever storms are waiting out there
Let them come for me.</i>

485
00:34:42.792 --> 00:34:47.583
<i>Whatever storms are waiting out there
Let them come for me.</i>

486
00:34:48.792 --> 00:34:51.917
<i>I'm done fighting fate
I'll drown before I flee.</i>

487
00:34:52.000 --> 00:34:55.500
Dad. my friends said
they're coming over for my birthday.

488
00:34:55.583 --> 00:34:56.500
Really?

489
00:34:56.583 --> 00:34:58.792
- Let's get a bigger cake.
- Okay.

490
00:34:58.958 --> 00:35:02.458
<i>I want everything. let it fall.</i>

491
00:35:02.917 --> 00:35:07.042
<i>I am torn. still I crawl.</i>

492
00:35:08.042 --> 00:35:12.250
<i>I want everything. let it fall.</i>

493
00:35:12.500 --> 00:35:14.458
<i>Still I crawl.</i>

494
