You can leave.

495
00:35:16.708 --> 00:35:17.833
I'll take care of it.

496
00:35:53.292 --> 00:35:55.542
<i>I want everything.</i>

497
00:35:58.083 --> 00:36:02.208
<i>I am torn. still I crawl.</i>

498
00:36:02.875 --> 00:36:05.208
<i>I want everything.</i>

499
00:36:05.375 --> 00:36:11.125
<i>Time is gone
And it's ripping out my heart.</i>

500
00:36:11.208 --> 00:36:18.167
<i>Whatever storms are waiting out there
Let them come for me.</i>

501
00:36:18.542 --> 00:36:23.292
<i>Whatever storms are waiting out there
Let them come for me.</i>

502
00:36:24.375 --> 00:36:28.583
<i>I'm done fighting fate
I'll drown before I flee.</i>

503
00:36:29.083 --> 00:36:30.500
It's all there. I counted it.

504
00:36:30.583 --> 00:36:32.625
<i>I want everything.</i>

505
00:36:32.917 --> 00:36:37.042
<i>Let it fall. I am torn.</i>

