507
00:36:40.250 --> 00:36:42.333
<i>I want everything.</i>

508
00:36:42.417 --> 00:36:46.167
<i>Let it fall. I am torn.</i>

509
00:36:46.250 --> 00:36:47.917
Take this 100-rupee note to Dubai.

510
00:36:48.375 --> 00:36:52.083
Deliver it to Justak Villa.
Street 14. Shihar. Dubai.

511
00:36:52.750 --> 00:36:55.751
They'll transfer the ten billion as
legitimate funds into the trust account.

512
00:36:55.792 --> 00:36:57.542
What about their contact details?

513
00:36:57.625 --> 00:36:59.167
I only deal with the mediator.

514
00:36:59.417 --> 00:37:01.500
The money will reach
the main dealer's account today.

515
00:37:01.750 --> 00:37:03.670
Nobody has the main dealer's
contact information.

516
00:37:03.792 --> 00:37:06.208
If you present the note
with the matching serial number.

517
00:37:06.458 --> 00:37:08.499
the money will be transferred
to your trust account.

518
00:37:14.542 --> 00:37:16.875
Sir. six months ago.

519
00:37:17.042 --> 00:37:20.833
Karthikeyan got us arrested
for smuggling sand from the lake.

520
00:37:20.917 --> 00:37:25.042
To get revenge. we killed him.
his wife. and his daughter.

521
00:37:25.208 --> 00:37:27.042
<i>We knew we'd get caught.</i>

522
00:37:27.542 --> 00:37:28.875
so we are surrendering.

523
00:37:29.000 --> 00:37:31.208
- Why are you all here?
- Move! Give way!

524
00:37:41.500 --> 00:37:43.083
- Hello. sir. Hello. ma'am.
- Hi. brother.

525
00:37:44.875 --> 00:37:46.833
- Let's go. brother.
- Hey. stop! Stop!

526
00:37:48.292 --> 00:37:50.750
I moved. so I'll be taking
this cab from now on.

527
00:37:51.375 --> 00:37:52.458
Okay. sir. Get in.

528
00:38:08.583 --> 00:38:10.167
You joined just a month ago. right?

529
00:38:12.167 --> 00:38:14.417
- How much is your salary?
- Thirty thousand. sir.

530
00:38:14.833 --> 00:38:15.917
Thirty thousand?

531
00:38:16.375 --> 00:38:17.542
It's too low. right?

532
00:38:20.000 --> 00:38:21.000
Don't worry.

533
00:38:21.208 --> 00:38:23.500
I'll make sure you get
a promotion soon.

534
00:38:24.000 --> 00:38:26.250
Here. your hard work doesn't matter.

535
00:38:27.042 --> 00:38:31.417
My reports to the higher-ups
about your hard work…

536
00:38:31.917 --> 00:38:32.958
That's important.

537
00:38:37.708 --> 00:38:39.500
Brother. pull over. please.

538
00:38:43.917 --> 00:38:44.917
Nila?

539
00:38:46.292 --> 00:38:47.833
Brother. unlock the door.

540
00:38:47.917 --> 00:38:50.625
How will you go home
alone at this hour?

541
00:38:51.375 --> 00:38:53.583
There are no buses on this route either.

542
00:38:55.875 --> 00:38:58.458
But I'm not the one
getting down. brother.

543
00:39:10.125 --> 00:39:12.542
Open the door!
Open the door. man!

544
00:39:12.667 --> 00:39:13.875
Unlock the door!

545
00:39:25.792 --> 00:39:26.792
Do it. now!

546
00:39:37.250 --> 00:39:38.750
Let's go. brother.

547
00:39:39.083 --> 00:39:41.542
I can't drop him off just anywhere
without permission.

548
00:39:41.750 --> 00:39:43.792
I'll check with him.

549
00:39:43.958 --> 00:39:45.417
Sir. are you coming with us.

550
00:39:45.667 --> 00:39:47.333
- or should I leave?
- No!

551
00:39:47.875 --> 00:39:48.875
I'll find my way.

552
00:39:49.083 --> 00:39:50.750
- You guys can leave.
- Thank you. sir.

553
00:40:03.042 --> 00:40:05.292
Do you want it
in big pieces or small ones?

554
00:40:06.125 --> 00:40:07.333
Cut it however you like.

555
00:40:07.625 --> 00:40:09.333
- You started?
- Yes.

556
00:40:09.875 --> 00:40:12.750
I'm visiting Thirunageswaram as well.
I'll be back in two days.

557
00:40:12.917 --> 00:40:13.792
Be careful.

558
00:40:13.875 --> 00:40:14.875
Okay.

559
00:40:15.125 --> 00:40:16.375
Don't close the shop.

560
00:40:16.458 --> 00:40:17.559
- Take turns and look after it.
- I'll take care of it.

561
00:40:17.583 --> 00:40:19.125
- Nila left for work?
- Yeah.

562
00:40:20.542 --> 00:40:23.417
God! He's pounded the carrots!

563
00:40:25.875 --> 00:40:26.875
Dear.

564
00:40:27.208 --> 00:40:28.542
Nila has a marriage proposal.

565
00:40:29.125 --> 00:40:31.000
The groom is working in NLC.

566
00:40:31.167 --> 00:40:32.292
They're related to us.

567
00:40:32.583 --> 00:40:36.333
They saw Nila
in Geetha's photo album.

568
00:40:37.625 --> 00:40:39.583
They're asking
if they can see her in person.

569
00:40:40.167 --> 00:40:41.167
Hey…

570
00:40:41.500 --> 00:40:42.833
She just got a job.

571
00:40:43.875 --> 00:40:46.292
These days. even if women get married.

572
00:40:46.708 --> 00:40:50.500
they should be bold enough and
trust themselves to live independently.

573
00:40:51.208 --> 00:40:52.969
Only an income will
give them the confidence.

574
00:40:53.042 --> 00:40:54.292
Let her work for some time.

575
00:40:54.583 --> 00:40:55.625
What's the hurry?

576
00:40:56.500 --> 00:40:59.667
God! Stop with your
boring philosophy class.

577
00:41:00.708 --> 00:41:03.458
I care about her too.
Just like you.

578
00:41:04.333 --> 00:41:07.417
Only if we start now
will we get a suitable groom for her.

579
00:41:08.167 --> 00:41:10.458
It's not like
we're marrying her off tomorrow.

580
00:41:11.042 --> 00:41:12.042
Look.

581
00:41:12.250 --> 00:41:14.375
Nila. you. and I.

582
00:41:15.042 --> 00:41:17.417
even if one of us doesn't like him.
let's call this off.

583
00:41:17.792 --> 00:41:18.792
Happy?

584
00:41:19.042 --> 00:41:20.042
No.

585
00:41:20.583 --> 00:41:23.125
It's not you. me. and her.

586
00:41:23.708 --> 00:41:25.029
Only Nila's opinion matters here.

587
00:41:25.708 --> 00:41:27.375
If she's okay with him.
we'll proceed.

588
00:41:29.000 --> 00:41:30.000
Okay.

589
00:41:30.208 --> 00:41:31.583
Only if she's okay with him.

590
00:41:31.958 --> 00:41:32.958
Happy?

591
00:41:33.167 --> 00:41:36.958
If the boy's family asks around.
they should only hear

592
00:41:37.208 --> 00:41:38.750
good things about her.

593
00:41:39.500 --> 00:41:41.000
So. please.

594
00:41:41.125 --> 00:41:43.542
Stop pouring oil
into that blazing fire.

595
00:41:45.250 --> 00:41:48.000
Or she might hit someone
without a thought.

596
00:41:48.250 --> 00:41:50.458
If she keeps inviting problems like these.

597
00:41:50.583 --> 00:41:53.458
we might as well forget her wedding.

598
00:41:54.750 --> 00:41:57.458
Let her learn to be patient
and considerate from now on.

599
00:41:58.333 --> 00:41:59.333
Okay.

600
00:42:05.125 --> 00:42:06.125
Weekly reports. bro.

601
00:42:09.125 --> 00:42:12.333
Looks like you sprained your neck
working last night.

602
00:42:16.917 --> 00:42:17.958
It's nothing like that.

603
00:42:18.333 --> 00:42:19.458
Stop your drama. bro.

604
00:42:19.625 --> 00:42:21.542
I saw you last night.

605
00:42:22.500 --> 00:42:23.500
What did you see?

606
00:42:24.250 --> 00:42:25.917
I saw the dancing car.

607
00:42:27.833 --> 00:42:29.375
Your car stopped midway on your route.

608
00:42:29.792 --> 00:42:31.083
Our cab crossed yours.

609
00:42:31.333 --> 00:42:33.375
Your cab was shaking vigorously.

610
00:42:35.792 --> 00:42:37.917
How did you pull her
in just a week?

611
00:42:39.208 --> 00:42:40.500
Oh. that?

612
00:42:41.625 --> 00:42:42.667
Yeah.

613
00:42:43.167 --> 00:42:44.167
She's easy.

614
00:42:44.917 --> 00:42:46.542
You just have to go talk to her.

615
00:42:47.042 --> 00:42:48.792
Why don't you try it out?

616
00:42:50.042 --> 00:42:51.042
Really?

617
00:42:51.292 --> 00:42:53.458
- Yeah.
- The moment I saw her. I knew

618
00:42:53.542 --> 00:42:54.667
she was a wild one.

619
00:42:56.458 --> 00:42:57.458
Wow!

620
00:42:57.625 --> 00:42:59.792
You've got a sharp eye for baddies.
just like me.

621
00:43:05.583 --> 00:43:07.000
- Hi. Nila.
- Hi.

622
00:43:08.917 --> 00:43:10.417
- Hi.
- Hello.

623
00:43:11.167 --> 00:43:12.167
That was superb. Nila.

624
00:43:15.667 --> 00:43:16.833
<i>Superb?</i>

625
00:43:18.583 --> 00:43:19.583
What's up. bro?

626
00:43:19.708 --> 00:43:21.458
Even your car was dancing?

627
00:43:22.792 --> 00:43:23.792
Yeah. bro.

628
00:43:27.667 --> 00:43:28.667
Superb. Nila.

629
00:43:29.042 --> 00:43:30.322
The cab driver told me about it.

630
00:43:45.875 --> 00:43:47.083
Please. sir.
Don't rat me out.

631
00:43:47.167 --> 00:43:48.792
Sir. drink and drive.

632
00:43:49.667 --> 00:43:51.347
Fine him and take the bike to the station.

633
00:43:51.583 --> 00:43:54.083
I only drank a little. sir.
Just let this slide. sir. Please.

634
00:43:54.667 --> 00:43:56.667
Sir. sorry. sir.
Please. don't do this. Sir…

635
00:43:56.750 --> 00:43:57.750
- Constable!
- Sir!

636
00:43:58.708 --> 00:44:00.250
Son. you can keep begging him.

637
00:44:02.042 --> 00:44:03.125
- Constable.
- Sir?

638
00:44:03.250 --> 00:44:05.708
After he's done begging.
tell him to take a rickshaw home.

639
00:44:06.625 --> 00:44:07.643
- Hey. come on.
- Sir. please.

640
00:44:07.667 --> 00:44:08.708
It's my dad's bike. sir.

641
00:44:08.833 --> 00:44:10.393
He'll kill me if I go home
without the bike.

642
00:44:10.417 --> 00:44:11.417
- I...
- You!

643
00:44:11.625 --> 00:44:12.750
Didn't you hear him?

644
00:44:12.833 --> 00:44:14.674
Come to the station in the morning.
Now. leave.

645
00:44:15.208 --> 00:44:17.083
Sir. I drank today for the first time.

646
00:44:17.208 --> 00:44:19.417
It's my birthday.
and my friends compelled me. sir.

647
00:44:19.625 --> 00:44:22.083
My house is just around the corner. sir.
Sir. please.

648
00:44:22.167 --> 00:44:23.643
- I swear I won't drink and drive. sir.
- Constable.

649
00:44:23.667 --> 00:44:24.542
- Sir.
- Get his license

650
00:44:24.625 --> 00:44:26.666
- and check his date of birth.
- Give me your license.

651
00:44:28.375 --> 00:44:29.375
What's your name?

652
00:44:29.417 --> 00:44:30.458
Saravana. sir.

653
00:44:30.875 --> 00:44:32.583
Sir. he's telling the truth.

654
00:44:36.000 --> 00:44:38.121
Alright. Just collect the fine.
Let him take the bike.

655
00:44:38.292 --> 00:44:40.000
Sir!
Don't give him the bike.

656
00:44:40.375 --> 00:44:42.536
- Sir. please.
- They'll learn only when they get caught.

657
00:44:42.708 --> 00:44:44.042
Sir. please. sir.

658
00:44:44.958 --> 00:44:45.958
Leave. man.

659
00:44:46.042 --> 00:44:46.917
- Get lost.
- Thank you. sir.

660
00:44:47.000 --> 00:44:48.292
Here. Go on.

661
00:44:50.333 --> 00:44:51.542
Hey. go.

662
00:45:02.167 --> 00:45:03.250
- Hey!
- What happened?

663
00:45:07.375 --> 00:45:08.833
- Hey. move.
- Make way.

664
00:45:09.375 --> 00:45:10.375
- Make way!
- Hey!

665
00:45:10.792 --> 00:45:12.083
- Hey!
- Hey!

666
00:45:12.958 --> 00:45:13.958
Hey!

667
00:45:18.542 --> 00:45:19.667
Sir. he's breathing.

668
00:45:20.375 --> 00:45:21.542
Get the car. Quick!

669
00:45:23.083 --> 00:45:24.958
That CCTV would've
recorded everything. sir.

670
00:45:25.583 --> 00:45:28.625
If anything happens to him.
they'll blame us.

671
00:45:28.917 --> 00:45:30.208
I told you. sir.

672
00:45:30.917 --> 00:45:32.357
I told you not to give him the bike.

673
00:45:58.042 --> 00:46:01.250
We need to get him out before
the police identify him.

674
00:46:01.708 --> 00:46:03.417
When the car hit the transformer.

675
00:46:03.833 --> 00:46:05.314
his head hit the steering wheel hard.

676
00:46:05.500 --> 00:46:06.917
That's why he went unconscious.

677
00:46:07.417 --> 00:46:10.000
He'll take a while to wake up.
But you need not worry.

678
00:46:10.250 --> 00:46:12.333
I've done a complete check-up.
He's safe.

679
00:46:18.500 --> 00:46:21.333
- Hey. keep moving.
- Get up. Be careful.

680
00:46:21.958 --> 00:46:23.417
- Move!
- Get out of here.

681
00:46:23.792 --> 00:46:24.792
- Go!
- Leave.

682
00:46:34.292 --> 00:46:35.292
Sir.

683
00:46:35.542 --> 00:46:36.792
they're looking at him.

684
00:46:38.167 --> 00:46:39.750
I think they're here to kill him.

685
00:46:40.750 --> 00:46:41.875
Hey. go.

686
00:46:46.208 --> 00:46:48.167
- Hey!
- Don't harm him. No!

687
00:46:59.042 --> 00:47:00.250
They're not here to kill him.

688
00:47:01.333 --> 00:47:02.625
They're here to take him away.

689
00:47:10.500 --> 00:47:13.292
Hey. he's just threatening us.
Go.

690
00:47:17.292 --> 00:47:18.167
Hey.

691
00:47:18.292 --> 00:47:19.750
There are 20 of us.

692
00:47:19.833 --> 00:47:21.792
How many can you take down
with six bullets?

693
00:47:22.125 --> 00:47:24.125
Even if you do.
you think the rest will let you go?

694
00:47:25.458 --> 00:47:26.500
Hey. go get him!

695
00:47:37.125 --> 00:47:38.333
Hey. wait. man!

696
00:47:38.500 --> 00:47:39.417
Don't do anything to him.

697
00:47:39.500 --> 00:47:41.458
- Bro. stop.
- Hey. leave me. man!

698
00:47:42.833 --> 00:47:46.375
- If something happens to him…
- Just go!

699
00:47:47.042 --> 00:47:48.667
Hey. come on! Let's go!

700
00:47:48.833 --> 00:47:50.708
Hey. Jeeva!
We will deal with him later.

701
00:47:50.917 --> 00:47:52.375
Guys. just get out of here.

702
00:47:55.875 --> 00:47:57.417
Listen to me.
Let's go.

703
00:48:08.667 --> 00:48:11.292
With all these men here for him.
he's up to something big.

704
00:48:18.667 --> 00:48:21.083
Take control of the hospital
until he wakes up.

705
00:48:25.833 --> 00:48:27.042
- Sir.
- Sir.

706
00:48:28.833 --> 00:48:30.875
- I'll try to find out who he is.
- Okay. sir.

707
00:48:30.958 --> 00:48:33.792
- Tell me as soon as he wakes up.
- Okay. sir.

708
00:48:35.375 --> 00:48:37.000
<i>It's an important transaction.</i>

709
00:48:37.500 --> 00:48:38.917
<i>Only he can complete it.</i>

710
00:48:39.458 --> 00:48:42.000
He shouldn't be under
police watch anymore.

711
00:48:42.583 --> 00:48:44.292
Send as many men as you want.

712
00:48:44.500 --> 00:48:46.042
They have to get him out!

713
00:48:56.875 --> 00:48:58.292
- Sir.
- I'll send you a photo.

714
00:48:58.375 --> 00:48:59.518
Forward it to all the stations.

715
00:48:59.542 --> 00:49:02.333
<i>- Check for history and criminal records.
- Yes. sir.</i>

716
00:49:08.125 --> 00:49:10.792
We're informing you because
she's from your area.

717
00:49:11.333 --> 00:49:12.833
Don't be hasty. Sundaram.

718
00:49:13.500 --> 00:49:14.917
I know them very well.

719
00:49:15.667 --> 00:49:17.125
<i>Sundaram's got murder charges.</i>

720
00:49:17.208 --> 00:49:18.583
And she's hit him and his men.

721
00:49:20.125 --> 00:49:22.208
<i>They were hell-bent on taking revenge.</i>

722
00:49:22.625 --> 00:49:24.417
<i>Thankfully. I came to know about this.</i>

723
00:49:24.708 --> 00:49:25.792
I sorted it out this time.

724
00:49:26.083 --> 00:49:27.958
But I can't keep doing this all the time.

725
00:49:28.125 --> 00:49:29.726
Ask your daughter to control her temper.

726
00:49:30.917 --> 00:49:31.958
I don't understand.

727
00:49:32.542 --> 00:49:35.083
How do you keep attracting trouble
wherever you go?

728
00:49:35.292 --> 00:49:37.542
- Mom. it's not...
- How many times do I have to tell you

729
00:49:37.625 --> 00:49:38.958
not to hit people?

730
00:49:39.667 --> 00:49:41.583
Should I keep following you around?

731
00:49:41.792 --> 00:49:44.500
Hey. did you ask whose fault it was?

732
00:49:45.083 --> 00:49:47.083
You! Just shut up!

733
00:49:47.417 --> 00:49:48.917
I don't want you to talk today.

734
00:49:50.083 --> 00:49:51.250
Are you mocking me?

735
00:49:51.375 --> 00:49:53.376
I did what you said.
and I'm still getting scolded?

736
00:49:53.750 --> 00:49:55.292
It's all because of you.

737
00:49:55.625 --> 00:49:57.875
You're the reason she's so rebellious.

738
00:49:58.792 --> 00:50:01.167
You'll understand only if she
gets into serious trouble.

739
00:50:01.458 --> 00:50:03.292
Who?
My daughter in trouble?

740
00:50:05.917 --> 00:50:06.917
Listen to me.

741
00:50:06.958 --> 00:50:10.208
If I hear one more complaint
that you hit someone.

742
00:50:10.917 --> 00:50:12.583
do not come in front of me again.

743
00:50:13.917 --> 00:50:17.042
The dad or the daughter?
Who do I deal with here?

744
00:50:18.583 --> 00:50:19.583
Nila.

745
00:50:23.958 --> 00:50:24.958
Yeah!

746
00:50:31.625 --> 00:50:32.625
Hello?

747
00:51:09.167 --> 00:51:10.167
Sir…

748
00:51:11.042 --> 00:51:12.042
Sir. take a look at this.

749
00:51:19.958 --> 00:51:21.042
How many were there?

750
00:51:22.250 --> 00:51:23.250
Sir.

751
00:51:23.958 --> 00:51:25.125
No one came. sir.

752
00:51:48.833 --> 00:51:50.333
Hey. look!
He opened his eyes.

753
00:51:50.417 --> 00:51:52.250
- Inform the officer that he's awake.
- Okay.

754
00:52:00.958 --> 00:52:02.958
<i>I don't talk much my entry is loud.</i>

755
00:52:03.042 --> 00:52:05.208
<i>Shadows move back
When I walk through crowds.</i>

756
00:52:05.292 --> 00:52:07.292
<i>Cold in my eyes. rage in control.</i>

757
00:52:07.417 --> 00:52:09.667
<i>One step deep
Yeah. I take your soul.</i>

758
00:52:18.417 --> 00:52:20.375
<i>No hero mask. no saving role.</i>

759
00:52:20.458 --> 00:52:22.583
<i>Straight villain mode
Heart made of stone.</i>

760
00:52:22.667 --> 00:52:24.792
<i>My silence hits harder
Than words you scream.</i>

761
00:52:24.875 --> 00:52:27.083
<i>When I step in frame
Whole city freeze</i>

762
00:52:27.167 --> 00:52:31.375
<i>I don't speak. I make endings
I don't smile. I leave bodies.</i>

763
00:52:31.458 --> 00:52:35.750
<i>Silent moves. deadly timing
One step forward. war's decided</i>

764
00:52:35.833 --> 00:52:40.167
<i>I don't speak. I make endings
I don't smile. I leave bodies.</i>

765
00:52:40.250 --> 00:52:44.542
<i>Silent moves. deadly timing
One step forward. war's decided.</i>

766
00:53:19.208 --> 00:53:20.375
Hey. run!

767
00:53:20.833 --> 00:53:21.875
- Hurry!
- Run!

768
00:53:27.083 --> 00:53:31.333
<i>No warning given. no second chance
Time runs out when I advance.</i>

769
00:53:31.417 --> 00:53:35.667
<i>Long my shadow. fear my rule
Enemies crumble. I stay cool.</i>

770
00:53:35.750 --> 00:53:40.042
<i>Stand against me. fate makes me
No path left just empty space.</i>

771
00:53:40.167 --> 00:53:45.292
<i>When I walk in. heroes reflow
Even the beat drops. heartbeat low.</i>

772
00:53:46.792 --> 00:53:48.750
<i>I don't talk much. my entry is loud.</i>

773
00:53:48.958 --> 00:53:51.042
<i>Shadows move back
When I walk through crowds.</i>

774
00:53:51.125 --> 00:53:53.167
<i>Cold in my eyes. rage in control.</i>

775
00:53:53.333 --> 00:53:55.333
<i>One step deep
Yeah. I take your soul.</i>

776
00:53:55.500 --> 00:53:57.542
<i>No hero mask. no saving role.</i>

777
00:53:57.625 --> 00:53:59.583
<i>Straight villain mode
Heart made of stone.</i>

778
00:53:59.667 --> 00:54:01.708
<i>My silence hits harder
Than words you scream.</i>

779
00:54:01.792 --> 00:54:04.125
<i>When I step in frame
Whole city freeze</i>

780
00:54:04.250 --> 00:54:08.500
<i>I don't speak. I make endings
I don't smile. I leave bodies.</i>

781
00:54:08.583 --> 00:54:12.875
<i>Silent moves. deadly timing
One step forward. war's decided</i>

782
00:54:12.958 --> 00:54:17.208
<i>I don't speak. I make endings
I don't smile. I leave bodies.</i>

783
00:54:17.292 --> 00:54:21.542
<i>Silent moves. deadly timing
One step forward. war's decided.</i>

784
00:54:21.625 --> 00:54:25.875
<i>No warning given. no second chance
Time runs out when I advance.</i>

785
00:54:25.958 --> 00:54:30.417
<i>Long my shadow. fear my rule
Enemies crumble. I stay cool.</i>

786
00:55:23.333 --> 00:55:25.083
The police are looking for you
everywhere.

787
00:55:25.917 --> 00:55:27.667
Right now. this is where
you'll be safe.

788
00:55:31.708 --> 00:55:32.792
I want to talk to Varun.

789
00:55:33.458 --> 00:55:35.792
I've got the 100-rupee note with me.

790
00:55:37.333 --> 00:55:40.125
Just arrange a private jet to Dubai.

791
00:55:40.542 --> 00:55:41.667
I'll stay here until then.

792
00:55:41.958 --> 00:55:43.333
- Just be ready.
<i>- Okay.</i>

793
00:55:46.000 --> 00:55:47.000
Nila.

794
00:55:48.250 --> 00:55:49.250
Nila?

795
00:55:51.875 --> 00:55:53.875
Don't feel bad that I'm shouting at you.

796
00:55:54.458 --> 00:55:55.500
Your dad

797
00:55:55.917 --> 00:55:59.125
might want you to
be brave and strong.

798
00:55:59.583 --> 00:56:00.583
But for me.

799
00:56:01.000 --> 00:56:04.375
I just want my daughter
to be happy and peaceful.

800
00:56:06.042 --> 00:56:08.000
You have to change yourself a little.

801
00:56:09.458 --> 00:56:13.875
You just have to understand one thing.

802
00:56:14.917 --> 00:56:17.375
There's no problem we can't solve
by talking it out.

803
00:56:18.208 --> 00:56:19.667
At least for my sake.

804
00:56:20.125 --> 00:56:22.125
don't fight with anyone.

805
00:56:23.458 --> 00:56:25.792
Think of it as my request.

806
00:56:29.000 --> 00:56:30.000
Okay. Mom.

807
00:56:36.750 --> 00:56:39.000
Hey. what if he refuses?

808
00:56:39.375 --> 00:56:40.935
I'll take care of it.
Just come with me.

809
00:56:42.625 --> 00:56:44.000
-Hello. brother.
-What's up. Kicha?

810
00:56:44.125 --> 00:56:46.958
Remember my friend who wanted
to join our gang?

811
00:56:47.042 --> 00:56:48.375
- Yeah.
- It's him.

812
00:56:48.792 --> 00:56:50.083
- Hello. brother.
- I see.

813
00:56:50.542 --> 00:56:51.917
- Brother's in a meeting.
- Okay.

814
00:56:52.000 --> 00:56:53.160
Wait here.
He'll be here soon.

815
00:56:53.333 --> 00:56:54.693
Come. buddy.
We'll wait over there.

816
00:56:56.083 --> 00:56:57.923
<i>Still. a bullet wound
is not an ordinary issue.</i>

817
00:56:58.167 --> 00:57:00.184
<i>If it gets infected.
we'll have to amputate your leg.</i>

818
00:57:00.208 --> 00:57:02.167
<i>You also said you strained your leg.</i>

819
00:57:02.708 --> 00:57:06.958
<i>If a nerve happens to get damaged.
your leg might get paralyzed.</i>

820
00:57:09.458 --> 00:57:11.333
<i>Alright. I'll write you
some tablets.</i>

821
00:57:11.583 --> 00:57:13.167
<i>Take them for a week.</i>

822
00:57:13.292 --> 00:57:15.583
<i>Else. you'll definitely
end up in a big problem.</i>

823
00:57:16.083 --> 00:57:19.042
<i>This tablet is meant for
post-bullet wound treatment.</i>

824
00:57:19.167 --> 00:57:21.750
<i>So. you won't get this
without a prescription.</i>

825
00:57:22.042 --> 00:57:23.333
I'll take care of it.

826
00:57:23.917 --> 00:57:25.250
Just tell me the tablet's name.

827
00:57:32.667 --> 00:57:33.667
Okay.

828
00:57:47.125 --> 00:57:48.708
Get me these tablets immediately.

829
00:57:49.458 --> 00:57:50.699
If they ask for a prescription.

830
00:57:51.958 --> 00:57:53.083
ask the guys to show this.

831
00:57:54.750 --> 00:57:55.750
- Shiva.
- Bro?

832
00:57:55.792 --> 00:57:57.417
- Where's Mani?
- He's downstairs.

833
00:58:00.792 --> 00:58:02.083
- Mani!
- Bro?

834
00:58:03.458 --> 00:58:04.833
- Come up.
- Coming!

835
00:58:06.792 --> 00:58:07.792
One minute.

836
00:58:08.583 --> 00:58:10.000
Send someone new.

837
00:58:10.333 --> 00:58:11.375
It's for your safety.

838
00:58:11.583 --> 00:58:13.167
Hey. wait.

839
00:58:16.542 --> 00:58:17.542
Hey.

840
00:58:18.042 --> 00:58:19.083
who's the new guy?

841
00:58:19.333 --> 00:58:21.083
Bro. he's my friend.

842
00:58:21.833 --> 00:58:25.000
I told you about my friend
who wanted to join our gang. right?

843
00:58:25.542 --> 00:58:26.792
- It's him.
- Bro.

844
00:58:29.000 --> 00:58:30.000
Shiva.

845
00:58:30.083 --> 00:58:31.083
how's he?

846
00:58:31.333 --> 00:58:32.583
Can he get things done?

847
00:58:32.958 --> 00:58:34.083
We don't even know him.

848
00:58:34.958 --> 00:58:35.958
Send him upstairs.

849
00:58:45.000 --> 00:58:46.000
Hello. brother.

850
00:58:46.292 --> 00:58:47.958
- What's your name?
- Toby.

851
00:58:48.333 --> 00:58:50.583
Kicha said you got out of prison
just two days ago.

852
00:58:50.667 --> 00:58:51.667
What did you do?

853
00:58:51.917 --> 00:58:53.417
A chain-snatching case. bro.

854
00:58:54.958 --> 00:58:57.375
I did it properly and came home.

855
00:58:58.167 --> 00:58:59.927
Even the police couldn't find out
who did it.

856
00:59:00.250 --> 00:59:02.083
Two weeks later.
once things cooled down.

857
00:59:02.167 --> 00:59:03.292
I sold it to a pawnbroker.

858
00:59:03.833 --> 00:59:06.083
But that moron ratted me out.

859
00:59:06.417 --> 00:59:09.792
They'll only fear us
if we beat them up a bit.

860
00:59:12.708 --> 00:59:14.167
As soon as I got released. I…

861
00:59:14.250 --> 00:59:16.458
Brother. forgive me.

862
00:59:16.625 --> 00:59:18.417
I won't do it again. bro.

863
00:59:18.625 --> 00:59:19.917
Please don't hurt me.

864
00:59:20.167 --> 00:59:22.125
God! Let me go. man.

865
00:59:23.292 --> 00:59:25.208
Please. brother. I'm sorry.

866
00:59:25.292 --> 00:59:26.932
- Call the police now.
- Brother. no. Don't!

867
00:59:36.500 --> 00:59:37.900
I have work for you.
Will you do it?

868
00:59:38.917 --> 00:59:39.917
Here.

869
00:59:40.375 --> 00:59:42.250
Go to a pharmacy
and get me this medicine.

870
00:59:48.958 --> 00:59:49.958
Nila.

871
00:59:51.292 --> 00:59:52.458
Dad's in the shop.

872
00:59:52.542 --> 00:59:54.833
I'll go and send him to eat.
Take care of the house.

873
00:59:55.333 --> 00:59:56.333
Alright. Mom.

874
01:00:05.125 --> 01:00:06.583
- Mom!
- Yes?

875
01:00:06.875 --> 01:00:07.875
What is it?

876
01:00:09.125 --> 01:00:10.125
You stay.

877
01:00:10.417 --> 01:00:11.292
I'll go.

878
01:00:11.375 --> 01:00:12.875
If they ask for a prescription.

879
01:00:14.083 --> 01:00:15.083
show this to them.

880
01:00:48.208 --> 01:00:49.208
Here you go. Dad.

881
01:01:04.208 --> 01:01:06.292
I'll call you later. Bye.

882
01:01:19.042 --> 01:01:20.417
Yes. sir?
What do you want?

883
01:01:29.667 --> 01:01:32.375
Sir. we can't give these medicines
without a prescription.

884
01:01:34.708 --> 01:01:36.292
Yeah. they told me.

885
01:01:43.000 --> 01:01:44.792
Still need a prescription?

886
01:01:55.417 --> 01:01:58.125
MOM

887
01:02:49.917 --> 01:02:54.083
Be a man. Pay him first.
then yell at me.

888
01:03:15.792 --> 01:03:17.875
Take off your chain.

889
01:03:25.083 --> 01:03:26.083
I won't.

890
01:03:26.833 --> 01:03:27.833
What was that?

891
01:03:30.083 --> 01:03:32.083
Do as I say.

892
01:03:33.792 --> 01:03:34.792
I won't.

893
01:03:35.167 --> 01:03:36.167
You've got some nerve!

894
01:03:36.750 --> 01:03:37.917
Say that to my face again!

895
01:03:43.042 --> 01:03:44.167
I won't…

896
01:03:49.917 --> 01:03:53.375
<i>Go ask around about me
Keep your pressure in check.</i>

897
01:03:54.000 --> 01:03:56.458
<i>Just say goodbye
To your folks already.</i>

898
01:03:57.083 --> 01:03:59.542
<i>There she stands Your boss!</i>

899
01:04:00.375 --> 01:04:02.333
<i>Bring your men
I'll make them run for their lives.</i>

900
01:04:02.417 --> 01:04:07.583
<i>Think you are the GOAT?
Be ready for a slaughter.</i>

901
01:04:07.667 --> 01:04:13.375
<i>Don't you dare. don't you dare
I'm lava. I'll burn you.</i>

902
01:04:13.458 --> 01:04:14.750
<i>Better be silent.</i>

903
01:04:14.833 --> 01:04:17.542
<i>You better take a U-turn
Save your life and better run.</i>

904
01:04:17.625 --> 01:04:20.708
<i>Don't let me catch you
I'll show you hell</i>

905
01:04:20.792 --> 01:04:23.833
<i>I may look like an angel
To you I'm the devil.</i>

906
01:04:23.958 --> 01:04:27.250
<i>Ten fingers are razor sharp
I'll shred you to pieces.</i>

907
01:04:41.000 --> 01:04:42.875
<i>Came from the underground.</i>

908
01:04:44.083 --> 01:04:45.708
<i>Fear never ever. son.</i>

909
01:04:46.792 --> 01:04:51.958
<i>I'm a monster here to eat you
Better be careful.</i>

910
01:05:04.500 --> 01:05:07.708
Sir. I checked every record.
There's no record of him.

911
01:05:09.625 --> 01:05:12.292
We haven't received any replies
to our faxes yet.

912
01:05:14.083 --> 01:05:15.683
It's been three hours
since the incident.

913
01:05:15.917 --> 01:05:18.375
and you want me to declare
we couldn't even find his name?

914
01:05:21.417 --> 01:05:23.250
- Ask them to speed up.
- Okay. sir.

915
01:05:32.333 --> 01:05:33.833
- Hello?
<i>- Hello. sir?</i>

916
01:05:34.042 --> 01:05:35.476
Yes. this is S1 Police Station.
Perambur.

917
01:05:35.500 --> 01:05:38.458
<i>Sir. we caught a guy
who tried to snatch a chain.</i>

918
01:05:38.625 --> 01:05:40.792
<i>- Can you come quickly?</i>
- Where exactly?

919
01:05:41.250 --> 01:05:43.333
<i>At Ilango Medicals near Sivan Park.</i>

920
01:05:43.458 --> 01:05:44.542
<i>Can you please hurry. sir?</i>

921
01:05:45.958 --> 01:05:46.958
We'll be there.

922
01:05:47.292 --> 01:05:48.458
Hurry up. we've got a case.

923
01:05:49.250 --> 01:05:50.531
We need to file a police report.

924
01:05:50.708 --> 01:05:52.917
Bring someone with you to the station.

925
01:05:53.333 --> 01:05:56.375
Okay. sir. My dad will take some time
to get there. I'll come with him.

926
01:05:56.542 --> 01:05:57.542
Alright.

927
01:05:57.583 --> 01:06:00.250
We'll take him to the hospital
in the meantime.

928
01:06:00.333 --> 01:06:01.654
Come to the station when you can.

929
01:06:01.708 --> 01:06:03.143
- Okay. sir.
- What are you doing here?

930
01:06:03.167 --> 01:06:04.042
Clear the place. everybody!

931
01:06:04.125 --> 01:06:05.125
Let's leave.

932
01:06:23.042 --> 01:06:25.792
Sir. we've blocked all checkpoints.

933
01:06:26.125 --> 01:06:28.250
There's no chance he left Chennai.

934
01:06:28.667 --> 01:06:30.627
Give me an hour's time.
and I'll scour thoroughly.

935
01:06:36.333 --> 01:06:38.333
Kicha. ring him up again.

936
01:06:38.500 --> 01:06:39.792
The boss wants to know.

937
01:06:40.042 --> 01:06:41.875
Bro. I tried.

938
01:06:42.250 --> 01:06:43.458
But his phone's switched off.

939
01:06:47.667 --> 01:06:48.667
Hello?

940
01:06:49.083 --> 01:06:50.083
Yes?

941
01:06:53.833 --> 01:06:55.083
I'll let you know when I do.

942
01:06:56.917 --> 01:06:58.167
- Sir…
- Alright.

943
01:06:58.500 --> 01:07:01.292
I really need to pee. sir.
Please.

944
01:07:01.417 --> 01:07:03.042
Use the one inside!

945
01:07:16.292 --> 01:07:17.458
Hello. Yes?

946
01:07:17.958 --> 01:07:18.958
Kicha.

947
01:07:19.500 --> 01:07:20.542
it's me. Toby.

948
01:07:21.125 --> 01:07:23.059
Where the hell are you. man?!
And whose number is this?

949
01:07:23.083 --> 01:07:24.500
Hand me the phone.

950
01:07:24.792 --> 01:07:26.312
<i>Hang on.
The boss wants to talk to you.</i>

951
01:07:29.417 --> 01:07:30.917
Where are you?

952
01:07:31.458 --> 01:07:33.375
I got caught by the police.

953
01:07:35.583 --> 01:07:36.833
<i>They don't know about it!</i>

954
01:07:37.333 --> 01:07:39.042
I've been arrested for chain snatching.

955
01:07:39.458 --> 01:07:41.750
What?!
When did this happen?

956
01:07:42.792 --> 01:07:43.875
A while ago.

957
01:07:44.458 --> 01:07:45.958
<i>What?! A while ago?</i>

958
01:07:46.042 --> 01:07:47.750
Did I send you out for that. you idiot?!

959
01:07:48.667 --> 01:07:52.250
Boss. there was a girl at Ilango Medicals

960
01:07:53.167 --> 01:07:54.458
near the park.

961
01:07:55.708 --> 01:07:58.375
I pulled a knife on her
to get your medicine.

962
01:07:59.667 --> 01:08:01.167
She gave it to me.

963
01:08:02.125 --> 01:08:04.458
But then I threatened her again

964
01:08:05.000 --> 01:08:08.167
to get her chain so I could
cover my household expenses.

965
01:08:13.208 --> 01:08:14.208
That's when…

966
01:08:19.208 --> 01:08:21.458
That's when she screamed.

967
01:08:21.708 --> 01:08:23.417
A crowd gathered. caught me.

968
01:08:23.667 --> 01:08:25.707
<i>and called the police
for attempted chain snatching.</i>

969
01:08:26.125 --> 01:08:27.583
They didn't know about the medicine

970
01:08:28.333 --> 01:08:30.094
and just assumed
I tried to snatch her chain.

971
01:08:31.583 --> 01:08:33.292
- Have they filed a police report?
- Not yet.

972
01:08:34.833 --> 01:08:35.833
The girl…

973
01:08:36.167 --> 01:08:37.667
They called her in to file one.

974
01:08:37.750 --> 01:08:39.875
But she said she'll come
with her father to do it.

975
01:08:41.125 --> 01:08:44.208
- What's taking you so long?
- Sir. sir! I'll be out in a minute!

976
01:08:44.292 --> 01:08:45.208
Well. hurry up!

977
01:08:45.292 --> 01:08:46.934
I'm talking on
one of the constables' phones.

978
01:08:46.958 --> 01:08:48.792
They're calling for me.
so don't call back.

979
01:08:54.708 --> 01:08:55.829
What are you thinking about?

980
01:08:57.583 --> 01:09:02.458
What if that girl tells the police
everything about the medicine.

981
01:09:03.000 --> 01:09:05.292
including what it was being used for?

982
01:09:06.042 --> 01:09:07.922
What if they figure out
that medicine is for me.

983
01:09:08.792 --> 01:09:11.458
torture him.
and he gives them your name?

984
01:09:12.625 --> 01:09:13.625
What will you do then?

985
01:09:15.458 --> 01:09:17.750
I'll be in Dubai tomorrow.
so I'm safe.

986
01:09:19.208 --> 01:09:21.625
You'll be the one in trouble.

987
01:09:23.250 --> 01:09:24.583
Eighteen cops have been killed.

988
01:09:26.958 --> 01:09:28.879
Those cops will go to any length
to hunt me down.

989
01:09:29.500 --> 01:09:30.667
Why don't we finish Toby?

990
01:09:32.000 --> 01:09:35.417
Going in and killing him
will only put us in deeper trouble.

991
01:09:36.125 --> 01:09:39.583
We'll be screwed if we mess with them.

992
01:09:40.333 --> 01:09:41.375
What do we do now?

993
01:09:42.125 --> 01:09:43.125
Velu bro?

994
01:09:43.208 --> 01:09:45.375
- Yes. Eli?
- Two cold beers. please.

995
01:09:45.458 --> 01:09:47.059
- Starters?
- Are you fine with Chintamani?

996
01:09:47.375 --> 01:09:49.625
Two plates of Chintamani Chicken
with extra pepper!

997
01:09:49.750 --> 01:09:50.625
On it!

998
01:09:50.708 --> 01:09:51.875
BROTHER KIRUBA.

999
01:09:52.875 --> 01:09:54.542
- Hello?
- Eli. where are you?

1000
01:09:54.833 --> 01:09:55.833
I'm nearby. boss.

1001
01:09:56.542 --> 01:09:59.417
I need information
on this girl right away.

1002
01:09:59.958 --> 01:10:02.125
Give me ten minutes.
I'll have it for you.

1003
01:10:04.208 --> 01:10:05.333
- Velu bro?
- Yes?

1004
01:10:05.458 --> 01:10:06.333
Cancel my order.

1005
01:10:06.417 --> 01:10:07.917
What's wrong?
It's almost ready!

1006
01:10:10.125 --> 01:10:12.208
Her dad's a karate master!

1007
01:10:12.458 --> 01:10:15.208
I can't hear you.
Step away from the speaker.

1008
01:10:15.417 --> 01:10:16.708
Karate master!

1009
01:10:17.042 --> 01:10:18.500
What?
I didn't catch that.

1010
01:10:19.542 --> 01:10:21.042
Karate master!

1011
01:10:21.417 --> 01:10:23.125
Oh. he's a headmaster!

1012
01:10:23.500 --> 01:10:25.500
Yes. that's what
I was trying to say. idiot!

1013
01:10:25.750 --> 01:10:27.167
Alright. man. Got it.

1014
01:10:27.250 --> 01:10:30.792
NEELAVENI RESIDENCE

1015
01:10:32.333 --> 01:10:33.667
- Nila?
- Yeah?

1016
01:10:34.000 --> 01:10:35.792
No matter what Mom says.
keep your cool.

1017
01:10:37.167 --> 01:10:38.542
Put on a sad face.

1018
01:10:41.250 --> 01:10:43.583
Got it. boss.
There are four people in the family.

1019
01:10:43.667 --> 01:10:45.375
It's her. her parents.
and her uncle.

1020
01:10:45.583 --> 01:10:47.643
<i>The uncle's out of town
and will be back in two days.</i>

1021
01:10:47.667 --> 01:10:49.268
<i>Her dad's a headmaster.
and her mom's a tailor.</i>

1022
01:10:49.292 --> 01:10:50.917
All three of them are home right now.

1023
01:10:51.083 --> 01:10:52.667
Now's our chance to kill them!

1024
01:10:52.792 --> 01:10:54.750
- They seem like a boring family.
- Okay. hang up.

1025
01:10:58.417 --> 01:11:01.458
- Let's not risk it. Finish them off.
- You got it.

1026
01:11:02.042 --> 01:11:07.208
Also. arrange for four of our men
to surrender afterward.

1027
01:11:07.667 --> 01:11:09.833
saying it was over a rejected love affair.

1028
01:11:10.083 --> 01:11:11.404
- Sure. Let's go. boys.
- Get going.

1029
01:11:27.167 --> 01:11:29.007
All this for an old couple
and a helpless girl?

1030
01:11:30.167 --> 01:11:31.767
Five guys are more than enough.
Let's go.

1031
01:11:47.667 --> 01:11:51.625
A man pulled a knife on her.
and you expect her to stay calm?

1032
01:11:51.833 --> 01:11:53.750
She didn't need to stand still.

1033
01:11:54.083 --> 01:11:57.458
but going that far wasn't right.

1034
01:11:58.167 --> 01:12:02.417
And when they come for her.
what will you do?

1035
01:12:03.875 --> 01:12:05.292
How will we find her a groom

1036
01:12:05.917 --> 01:12:08.083
if we're shuttling between
police stations and cases?

1037
01:12:08.375 --> 01:12:09.375
Enough!

1038
01:12:09.917 --> 01:12:13.458
Go to them. drop the case.

1039
01:12:13.583 --> 01:12:15.184
- and be done with it.
- Fine. we'll do it.

1040
01:12:18.000 --> 01:12:20.583
Pretty packed neighborhood.
Let's be quick with it.

1041
01:12:20.667 --> 01:12:21.667
Yes. boss.

1042
01:12:49.917 --> 01:12:50.917
Ready. Nila?

1043
01:12:51.542 --> 01:12:52.583
In a minute. Dad.

1044
01:14:28.500 --> 01:14:29.500
Kill them.

1045
01:16:40.875 --> 01:16:44.042
Remember the guy from the medical shop?
Maybe they are his men.

1046
01:16:52.083 --> 01:16:53.625
Call the police immediately!

1047
01:16:54.750 --> 01:16:58.833
You want to snitch on us
for killing three men?

1048
01:16:59.583 --> 01:17:02.708
What if we tell them
they slipped and fell to their deaths?

1049
01:17:03.542 --> 01:17:06.042
They fell together?

1050
01:17:06.917 --> 01:17:09.000
I'll take the blame
and serve time. then.

1051
01:17:09.625 --> 01:17:11.000
Call them at once!

1052
01:17:14.833 --> 01:17:17.833
I'm sure he will snitch on us.

1053
01:17:20.625 --> 01:17:21.667
What do we do. Dad?

1054
01:17:22.833 --> 01:17:23.833
It's over…

1055
01:17:24.000 --> 01:17:26.958
Our family. our peace…
It's all gone to ruin!

1056
01:17:47.500 --> 01:17:48.542
I have an idea.

1057
01:17:52.917 --> 01:17:54.458
Let this be between us.

1058
01:17:56.042 --> 01:17:57.375
We'll bury them…

1059
01:17:58.083 --> 01:17:59.792
In that hole in the backyard.

1060
01:18:07.625 --> 01:18:08.625
What about him…

1061
01:18:09.708 --> 01:18:11.458
And the other two who are hiding?

1062
01:18:17.583 --> 01:18:18.583
Everybody!

1063
01:18:24.708 --> 01:18:25.708
Dear…

1064
01:18:26.875 --> 01:18:28.875
Anyone who comes after my daughter

1065
01:18:30.042 --> 01:18:31.667
won't leave alive.

1066
01:18:35.167 --> 01:18:37.417
I know how you do things
for her sake.

1067
01:18:38.667 --> 01:18:39.833
This is also for her.

1068
01:19:04.125 --> 01:19:09.292
<i>The low-pressure system formed
over the Bay of Bengal is intensifying…</i>

1069
01:19:33.208 --> 01:19:34.292
Hey. let's get them.

1070
01:20:00.667 --> 01:20:02.792
Isn't he a headmaster?

1071
01:20:17.458 --> 01:20:18.458
What are you looking for?

1072
01:20:18.958 --> 01:20:20.292
My wallet that was in my pocket.

1073
01:20:22.500 --> 01:20:24.833
Bro. was it a brown one?

1074
01:20:25.750 --> 01:20:29.208
- Yeah.
- It fell when you were on the phone.

1075
01:20:29.375 --> 01:20:31.375
I kept it here
thinking you'd be back.

1076
01:20:33.250 --> 01:20:34.750
Hey. I kept it here…

1077
01:20:36.125 --> 01:20:37.250
It was right here. man.

1078
01:20:37.917 --> 01:20:40.333
- Where is it now?
- It was right here…

1079
01:20:41.750 --> 01:20:42.792
Search. boys.

1080
01:20:43.125 --> 01:20:46.333
- Over there. too!
- I clearly remember leaving it there.

1081
01:20:47.000 --> 01:20:48.125
Where is it?

1082
01:20:57.917 --> 01:20:59.500
- Check under the chairs.
- Bro!

1083
01:20:59.958 --> 01:21:02.333
Is this it?
It was in your car.

1084
01:21:02.417 --> 01:21:04.577
- See. I knew it had to be around…
- Yes. that's the one.

1085
01:21:12.000 --> 01:21:13.750
Hey. that's my brother's.

1086
01:21:47.375 --> 01:21:48.958
Call Shiva right now.

1087
01:21:53.000 --> 01:21:54.000
Boss.

1088
01:21:54.375 --> 01:21:56.417
why is he so tense
about a missing wallet?

1089
01:21:57.042 --> 01:21:58.875
It isn't just a wallet.

1090
01:22:01.375 --> 01:22:02.583
It's a deal worth ten billion!

1091
01:22:09.792 --> 01:22:11.833
It'll be finalized in two days.

1092
01:22:12.708 --> 01:22:15.708
Using the 60 billion profit
it brings us.

1093
01:22:16.042 --> 01:22:18.833
ask the research team to pull up a list

1094
01:22:19.292 --> 01:22:23.917
of potential mining places to invest in.

1095
01:22:24.167 --> 01:22:25.458
- Okay. sir.
- Okay. sir!

1096
01:22:32.417 --> 01:22:35.167
Sixty billion!

1097
01:22:59.792 --> 01:23:02.042
Bro. no one's answering.

1098
01:23:06.167 --> 01:23:07.667
No one's answering?

1099
01:23:08.667 --> 01:23:09.958
Something's not right.

1100
01:23:11.458 --> 01:23:15.083
Abraham. it's not safe here.
Let's move.

1101
01:23:35.500 --> 01:23:37.500
And make sure that
the file is on my table by ten.

1102
01:23:38.500 --> 01:23:39.701
I'll see you tomorrow morning.

1103
01:23:40.125 --> 01:23:41.125
Good evening. sir.

1104
01:24:00.750 --> 01:24:01.750
Vincent!

1105
01:24:11.917 --> 01:24:12.917
Hi. sir.

1106
01:24:14.958 --> 01:24:15.958
Welcome. Sridhar.

1107
01:24:16.292 --> 01:24:17.532
They said you wanted to see me.

1108
01:24:17.917 --> 01:24:18.917
How can I help you. sir?

1109
01:24:20.417 --> 01:24:22.125
Last evening.
where were you. Sridhar?

1110
01:24:22.667 --> 01:24:23.958
I was at home. sir. Why?

1111
01:24:24.708 --> 01:24:26.042
- Is that so?
- Yes. sir.

1112
01:24:26.458 --> 01:24:32.167
I heard you met with Guru Ram.
the MD of VRS. last night.

1113
01:24:33.000 --> 01:24:34.125
Is that just a rumor?

1114
01:24:37.375 --> 01:24:40.708
It's a massive project. sir.
Varun's making a move on it.

1115
01:24:41.250 --> 01:24:43.333
The profit is around 70 billion.

1116
01:24:43.708 --> 01:24:47.833
Offer the Mining Minister a bigger cut.

1117
01:24:48.125 --> 01:24:49.833
and get him to hand it to you.

1118
01:24:51.083 --> 01:24:52.083
No. sir.

1119
01:24:52.750 --> 01:24:54.875
I didn't meet anyone.

1120
01:25:02.833 --> 01:25:03.833
Then who's this?

1121
01:25:12.250 --> 01:25:16.042
So you told him about the.

1122
01:25:16.208 --> 01:25:19.458
Keelakadu mining project and its value.

1123
01:25:19.542 --> 01:25:20.792
- Sir…
- Am I right?

1124
01:25:22.083 --> 01:25:23.583
Sir…
No. sir.

1125
01:25:24.833 --> 01:25:25.833
No. sir.

1126
01:25:27.042 --> 01:25:28.042
Sir. please.

1127
01:25:28.917 --> 01:25:30.000
I feel sorry for him.

1128
01:25:30.792 --> 01:25:32.542
<i>You shouldn't have told him that.</i>

1129
01:25:37.667 --> 01:25:39.875
Sir. please… forgive me. sir.

1130
01:25:40.208 --> 01:25:41.208
It won't happen again.

1131
01:25:41.375 --> 01:25:42.750
Please. sir.

1132
01:25:43.333 --> 01:25:44.684
Sir. please…
It won't happen again.

1133
01:25:44.708 --> 01:25:45.958
Sir. please.

1134
01:25:46.042 --> 01:25:49.917
If you knew how much this project
meant to me and the company.

1135
01:25:50.250 --> 01:25:51.691
you wouldn't have opened your mouth.

1136
01:25:51.792 --> 01:25:52.792
Sir. please.

1137
01:26:03.667 --> 01:26:05.292
Eli. that's as cold as it gets.

1138
01:26:05.917 --> 01:26:07.184
The chicken's nearly done.
I'll get it.

1139
01:26:07.208 --> 01:26:08.208
Make it quick. Velu bro.

1140
01:26:12.542 --> 01:26:13.875
- Yeah. bro.
- Hey. Eli.

1141
01:26:14.208 --> 01:26:15.208
something's wrong.

1142
01:26:15.583 --> 01:26:17.059
We haven't heard from
the guys we sent for the hit.

1143
01:26:17.083 --> 01:26:18.524
and no one's answering their phones.

1144
01:26:18.750 --> 01:26:19.875
<i>Go check out that house.</i>

1145
01:26:19.958 --> 01:26:20.958
Got it. brother.

1146
01:26:21.208 --> 01:26:22.833
- Velu bro. Cancel the beer.
- Yeah.

1147
01:26:31.667 --> 01:26:33.507
All this for an old couple
and a helpless girl?

1148
01:26:33.792 --> 01:26:35.392
<i>Five guys are more than enough.
Let's go.</i>

1149
01:26:37.792 --> 01:26:39.000
- Hey!
- Brother. be careful!

1150
01:26:40.083 --> 01:26:41.583
- Hey.
- Hey. what's wrong?

1151
01:26:45.750 --> 01:26:47.500
We've got a nail in the tire.

1152
01:26:47.667 --> 01:26:49.042
The house is only two blocks away.

1153
01:26:50.167 --> 01:26:51.917
There's no time.
Let's walk.

1154
01:27:05.458 --> 01:27:07.619
They must be waiting for us
at the police station. Dad.

1155
01:27:11.875 --> 01:27:13.708
If we get dragged into a legal fight.

1156
01:27:14.750 --> 01:27:16.125
we're the ones who'll pay for it.

1157
01:27:18.250 --> 01:27:19.500
As your mom said.

1158
01:27:20.250 --> 01:27:21.250
let's drop the case.

1159
01:27:24.667 --> 01:27:25.667
Let's go. Dad.

1160
01:27:45.458 --> 01:27:47.125
What time did I call him?

1161
01:27:47.333 --> 01:27:49.500
- Around eight.
- Eight o'clock.

1162
01:27:49.667 --> 01:27:51.792
They probably headed out
ten minutes later.

1163
01:27:52.208 --> 01:27:53.851
Another ten to reach
the spot where the tire blew.

1164
01:27:53.875 --> 01:27:55.976
If they went the rest of the way on foot.
another five minutes.

1165
01:27:56.000 --> 01:27:58.042
But there's no sign
of our guys at that house.

1166
01:27:58.125 --> 01:28:00.542
Thunder. wind. and heavy rain…
What do you make of it?

1167
01:28:02.333 --> 01:28:03.333
Confirmed.

1168
01:28:04.208 --> 01:28:05.208
Give me the phone.

1169
01:28:05.500 --> 01:28:08.250
Bro. our guys
never made it to the house.

1170
01:28:08.500 --> 01:28:09.958
What are you talking about?

1171
01:28:10.333 --> 01:28:12.125
Someone planted
a nail two blocks away.

1172
01:28:12.208 --> 01:28:14.667
blew their tire.
and grabbed them.

1173
01:28:15.125 --> 01:28:16.167
What do you mean?

1174
01:28:16.333 --> 01:28:18.375
Yes.
I checked the house.

1175
01:28:18.542 --> 01:28:20.667
If our guys had made it.
that family would be dead.

1176
01:28:21.000 --> 01:28:23.542
But they're just sitting there
watching a soap opera.

1177
01:28:23.833 --> 01:28:25.083
<i>Something's wrong.</i>

1178
01:28:33.625 --> 01:28:34.708
Hey. it's brother.

1179
01:28:36.500 --> 01:28:37.375
Yes. brother.

1180
01:28:37.458 --> 01:28:40.792
Give me a list of anyone who planned
a hit on Shiva in the last month.

1181
01:28:41.292 --> 01:28:42.292
What's wrong?

1182
01:28:42.708 --> 01:28:43.833
I'll fill you in later.

1183
01:28:44.250 --> 01:28:46.208
Just get me those names first.

1184
01:28:46.292 --> 01:28:47.625
<i>Hold on a second.</i>

1185
01:28:48.292 --> 01:28:51.292
- What?
- A cop came by looking for him.

1186
01:28:51.417 --> 01:28:53.250
Some idiot broke
into the go down and ran off

1187
01:28:53.333 --> 01:28:54.958
with the seized half kilo of marijuana.

1188
01:28:55.083 --> 01:28:57.434
I have to produce the seized material
in court on Monday morning.

1189
01:28:57.458 --> 01:28:59.833
A guy's brought some stuff
into Ayanavaram.

1190
01:29:00.250 --> 01:29:01.500
Tell him that I sent you.

1191
01:29:01.833 --> 01:29:02.873
He'll definitely help you.

1192
01:29:02.958 --> 01:29:05.083
- Alright. Give me his details.
- It's Shiva.

1193
01:29:05.583 --> 01:29:06.583
I'm here for Shiva.

1194
01:29:11.500 --> 01:29:13.000
He's out on a job.

1195
01:29:13.167 --> 01:29:14.458
Won't be back for an hour.

1196
01:29:14.667 --> 01:29:16.707
You can tell me what it's about.
I'll pass it along.

1197
01:29:17.083 --> 01:29:19.625
No. I'll come back later.

1198
01:29:19.792 --> 01:29:22.583
Just tell him SI Udhaya
from S1 Station stopped by.

1199
01:29:25.000 --> 01:29:26.667
- The cops came by?
- Yeah. brother.

1200
01:29:26.792 --> 01:29:29.417
Said he's from
the Perambur S1 Station.

1201
01:29:29.583 --> 01:29:31.083
<i>but he didn't say what it was about.</i>

1202
01:29:35.583 --> 01:29:38.292
- Where are you?
- I'm at Perambur S1 Station.

1203
01:29:39.208 --> 01:29:41.833
What if they torture him
and he gives them your name?

1204
01:29:41.917 --> 01:29:43.875
<i>Those cops will go to any length
to hunt me down.</i>

1205
01:29:44.125 --> 01:29:46.042
A cop came by looking for him.

1206
01:29:46.917 --> 01:29:48.708
Someone planted
a nail two blocks away.

1207
01:29:48.792 --> 01:29:51.000
blew their tire.
and grabbed them.

1208
01:29:51.833 --> 01:29:52.958
S1 Police Station.

1209
01:29:53.250 --> 01:29:55.042
Said he's from
the Perambur S1 Station.

1210
01:29:55.125 --> 01:29:57.125
Blew their tire
and grabbed them.

1211
01:29:57.292 --> 01:29:59.250
Those cops will go to any length
to hunt me down.

1212
01:30:02.167 --> 01:30:07.250
<i>S1… Police Station.</i>

1213
01:30:07.458 --> 01:30:09.125
Toby must've told the cops everything.

1214
01:30:11.375 --> 01:30:13.417
They got to my brother
just to get to you.

1215
01:30:19.667 --> 01:30:20.667
Brother?

1216
01:30:21.000 --> 01:30:22.000
Yeah. brother.

1217
01:30:30.208 --> 01:30:31.208
Sir.

1218
01:30:31.458 --> 01:30:32.333
Yes?

1219
01:30:32.417 --> 01:30:34.297
I need to see the inspector
about a permit. sir.

1220
01:30:34.583 --> 01:30:36.000
- Go meet the constable.
- Okay.

1221
01:30:36.417 --> 01:30:37.417
What a headache.

1222
01:30:39.625 --> 01:30:42.625
Go get their signature.
Then I'll tell you what to do next.

1223
01:30:57.292 --> 01:30:58.292
Hey!

1224
01:30:58.333 --> 01:30:59.333
What do you want?

1225
01:30:59.500 --> 01:31:03.250
Sir. I'm here to see the inspector
about a banner permit.

1226
01:31:03.667 --> 01:31:05.226
You can't see him today.
Come back tomorrow.

1227
01:31:05.250 --> 01:31:06.250
Okay. sir.

1228
01:31:17.542 --> 01:31:18.542
Hello. sir.

1229
01:31:18.917 --> 01:31:20.797
Your brother and our guys
aren't at the station.

1230
01:31:21.083 --> 01:31:22.803
<i>I think they're holding them
somewhere else.</i>

1231
01:31:30.000 --> 01:31:32.583
They moved them
since it's not safe at the station.

1232
01:31:33.125 --> 01:31:36.125
Bro. they're one step ahead of us.

1233
01:31:37.125 --> 01:31:39.917
We have to find out
where they're holding him.

1234
01:31:46.917 --> 01:31:48.750
Do you take us for fools?

1235
01:31:49.000 --> 01:31:51.583
We're supposed
to arrest them on your word

1236
01:31:51.667 --> 01:31:53.917
and then drop the charges
when you change your mind?

1237
01:31:54.583 --> 01:31:57.333
It's because people like you
are so easily intimidated

1238
01:31:57.417 --> 01:31:59.257
that guys like him
keep getting away with this.

1239
01:31:59.333 --> 01:32:00.542
POLICE CLERK

1240
01:32:00.708 --> 01:32:02.375
Why are you acting like a coward?

1241
01:32:03.167 --> 01:32:05.917
Sir. I have a daughter.

1242
01:32:06.917 --> 01:32:10.292
My wife's terrified of getting involved
with people like this.

1243
01:32:11.708 --> 01:32:14.208
At the end of the day.
my family comes first. sir.

1244
01:32:14.958 --> 01:32:16.125
Let's drop the case.

1245
01:32:17.083 --> 01:32:19.375
I'm scared too.

1246
01:32:22.042 --> 01:32:23.250
You heard him.

1247
01:32:24.000 --> 01:32:26.801
Get a statement confirming that
it was their decision to drop the case.

1248
01:32:26.917 --> 01:32:27.917
Okay. sir.

1249
01:32:29.708 --> 01:32:30.708
This one…

1250
01:32:31.917 --> 01:32:33.518
Charge him with
public nuisance under Section 75

1251
01:32:33.542 --> 01:32:35.462
- and send him in for a 15-day remand.
- Okay. sir.

1252
01:32:37.375 --> 01:32:40.125
You'd better come in
and sign it. Understand?

1253
01:32:41.042 --> 01:32:42.042
Wait.

1254
01:32:42.875 --> 01:32:44.292
Inform the inspector first.

1255
01:32:44.750 --> 01:32:45.750
Okay. sir.

1256
01:32:47.708 --> 01:32:48.708
What's your name?

1257
01:32:49.042 --> 01:32:50.042
Nila.

1258
01:32:50.167 --> 01:32:51.167
Hey. come here.

1259
01:32:56.667 --> 01:32:57.667
Tell me your name.

1260
01:32:58.250 --> 01:32:59.125
Toby.

1261
01:32:59.250 --> 01:33:00.375
Sign here.

1262
01:33:08.750 --> 01:33:09.750
Sir.

1263
01:33:10.458 --> 01:33:12.042
Sir. it's a chain-snatching case.

1264
01:33:12.542 --> 01:33:14.458
but they want to drop the charges...

1265
01:33:16.292 --> 01:33:17.292
Hello.

1266
01:33:17.667 --> 01:33:19.907
- Where are you keeping my brother?
- Who the hell is this?

1267
01:33:20.042 --> 01:33:21.833
I'm the brother
of the man you took.

1268
01:33:22.625 --> 01:33:23.958
And who exactly is that?

1269
01:33:24.083 --> 01:33:25.208
My brother!

1270
01:33:25.500 --> 01:33:28.583
Look. I'm already on edge.

1271
01:33:29.125 --> 01:33:32.000
You've got the wrong guy.
Just hang up.

1272
01:33:32.083 --> 01:33:34.792
I know you grabbed my brother
and five others

1273
01:33:34.875 --> 01:33:37.315
to find the guy who escaped
from your custody at the hospital.

1274
01:33:37.792 --> 01:33:40.083
Torture them all you want.

1275
01:33:40.625 --> 01:33:42.500
but they won't break.

1276
01:33:42.667 --> 01:33:44.267
<i>But your son isn't as tough as they are.</i>

1277
01:33:44.542 --> 01:33:46.833
<i>One twist of a screwdriver</i>

1278
01:33:47.125 --> 01:33:48.405
and he's screaming for his life.

1279
01:33:48.625 --> 01:33:50.292
<i>I sent you a video on WhatsApp.</i>

1280
01:33:51.208 --> 01:33:52.329
Watch it and get back to me.

1281
01:33:54.500 --> 01:33:55.500
<i>Brother. no!</i>

1282
01:33:55.542 --> 01:33:57.208
Please. don't!

1283
01:33:57.292 --> 01:33:59.500
- Let me go! Please!
- Hari! No!

1284
01:33:59.583 --> 01:34:01.917
- I'm scared! Please. brother.
- Please. sir! Please!

1285
01:34:02.000 --> 01:34:03.000
Brother. no!

1286
01:34:03.042 --> 01:34:04.667
- No!
- It's going to hurt.

1287
01:34:04.750 --> 01:34:06.917
- Please. sir!
- Tell him to stop! Please. brother!

1288
01:34:07.125 --> 01:34:09.500
It's going to hurt! Please!

1289
01:34:14.833 --> 01:34:16.958
- Hari.
- It hurts. brother!

1290
01:34:22.750 --> 01:34:25.583
So you don't have my brother?

1291
01:34:25.750 --> 01:34:27.470
I'm telling you the truth.
I don't have him!

1292
01:34:28.000 --> 01:34:30.333
You saw the screwdriver
in your kid's hand.

1293
01:34:31.083 --> 01:34:33.208
You still care more about your badge?

1294
01:34:33.292 --> 01:34:34.875
<i>- Idiot.</i>
- You fool!

1295
01:34:35.583 --> 01:34:37.750
Don't you get it?
You've got the wrong man!

1296
01:34:38.125 --> 01:34:40.417
Hey. enough with the act.

1297
01:34:41.083 --> 01:34:44.708
I know you've got Toby in custody.
and he's already talked.

1298
01:34:44.833 --> 01:34:47.500
Toby? In my custody?

1299
01:34:47.583 --> 01:34:49.250
ACCUSED NAME: TOBY
AGE: 36

1300
01:34:49.375 --> 01:34:51.000
Listen carefully.

1301
01:34:51.792 --> 01:34:53.792
My men are waiting
by the Ennore Lighthouse.

1302
01:34:53.875 --> 01:34:55.458
You have exactly one hour.

1303
01:34:55.542 --> 01:34:57.500
Bring my brother
and the other five there.

1304
01:34:57.583 --> 01:34:59.500
If you don't. that screwdriver's

1305
01:34:59.917 --> 01:35:02.625
going through your wife's
and son's heads in the next video.

1306
01:35:02.708 --> 01:35:03.949
I'm telling you. I don't have...

1307
01:35:08.083 --> 01:35:09.125
Head to our spot.

1308
01:35:12.875 --> 01:35:14.708
- Where's this Toby?
- He's right outside. sir.

1309
01:35:34.500 --> 01:35:35.667
Sir! Please. sir!

1310
01:35:35.750 --> 01:35:37.500
-You're going to answer.
-Sir…

1311
01:35:37.583 --> 01:35:38.833
All my questions now.

1312
01:35:39.417 --> 01:35:43.125
I'll talk! I'll tell you everything!

1313
01:35:43.250 --> 01:35:45.875
<i>I know you grabbed my brother
and five others</i>

1314
01:35:45.958 --> 01:35:47.684
<i>to find the guy who escaped
from your custody…</i>

1315
01:35:47.708 --> 01:35:48.708
Whose voice is this?

1316
01:35:49.375 --> 01:35:50.542
It's Kirubakaran's voice.

1317
01:35:51.042 --> 01:35:53.458
- Who is he?
- A gangster out of Perambur. sir.

1318
01:35:53.917 --> 01:35:55.583
- What's his brother's name?
- Shiva.

1319
01:35:55.708 --> 01:35:57.542
- Where is he?
- I don't know. sir!

1320
01:35:57.958 --> 01:36:00.184
- You expect me to believe that? Do you?
- I'm telling the truth!

1321
01:36:00.208 --> 01:36:01.667
I swear to God!

1322
01:36:01.792 --> 01:36:04.333
- I'm telling the truth!
- Sir. sir! Stop!

1323
01:36:05.667 --> 01:36:06.667
Sir.

1324
01:36:09.208 --> 01:36:10.083
What's going on?

1325
01:36:10.167 --> 01:36:12.958
Someone snatched his brother
and five of his men.

1326
01:36:13.833 --> 01:36:16.917
He thinks I did it.
so he took my wife and son!

1327
01:36:17.333 --> 01:36:19.854
He says if I don't release his brother.
he's going to kill them!

1328
01:36:25.000 --> 01:36:26.333
Ahmed. Suresh. Gopi. and Muthu.

1329
01:36:26.417 --> 01:36:28.333
go track down Kirubakaran.

1330
01:36:28.417 --> 01:36:29.417
- Okay. sir.
- Okay. sir.

1331
01:36:29.625 --> 01:36:30.934
Kannan. Pachamuthu. Bala. and Vinoth.

1332
01:36:30.958 --> 01:36:33.208
get Shiva's number
and track his location.

1333
01:36:33.333 --> 01:36:34.333
- Okay. sir.
- Okay. sir.

1334
01:36:38.167 --> 01:36:40.542
You guys leave. We've got
something else to deal with.

1335
01:36:43.042 --> 01:36:44.958
I've guaranteed the funds
will hit the account

1336
01:36:45.250 --> 01:36:46.650
the minister specified by tomorrow.

1337
01:36:47.667 --> 01:36:51.417
There's a snag
with the private jet's landing.

1338
01:36:51.667 --> 01:36:55.083
<i>so I'm sending my manager to Dubai
on a commercial flight instead.</i>

1339
01:36:55.250 --> 01:36:56.750
My manager's coming to see you.

1340
01:36:57.208 --> 01:36:59.000
Give him the hundred-rupee note.

1341
01:36:59.750 --> 01:37:01.542
He'll handle things in Dubai.

1342
01:37:03.958 --> 01:37:05.875
Alright. send him over.

1343
01:37:10.750 --> 01:37:11.750
Hello. tell me.

1344
01:37:12.167 --> 01:37:15.042
Sir. Shiva's phone
has been off for the past hour.

1345
01:37:15.333 --> 01:37:18.083
<i>The last ping we got
was near Perambur Periyar Bridge.</i>

1346
01:37:18.167 --> 01:37:20.417
- We're heading there now.
- Keep me posted.

1347
01:37:20.500 --> 01:37:21.500
<i>Okay. sir.</i>

1348
01:37:38.625 --> 01:37:41.059
Why didn't you just tell Varun
you don't have the hundred-rupee note?

1349
01:37:41.083 --> 01:37:42.792
You want me to tell him

1350
01:37:42.875 --> 01:37:45.235
that your brother grabbed
the wrong wallet and went missing?

1351
01:37:46.750 --> 01:37:48.000
You think he'll buy that?

1352
01:37:48.208 --> 01:37:51.458
He'll think you're playing games
over a billion dollars and take you out.

1353
01:37:52.458 --> 01:37:53.458
Is that what you want?

1354
01:37:57.917 --> 01:38:01.250
He might think I'm in on it. too.

1355
01:38:05.417 --> 01:38:08.875
Have one of our guys keep a close eye
on the inspector's every move.

1356
01:38:08.958 --> 01:38:09.958
Okay. bro.

1357
01:38:12.542 --> 01:38:13.417
Hello. who's this?

1358
01:38:13.500 --> 01:38:15.417
This is Manimaaran.
Commissioner of Trichy.

1359
01:38:15.500 --> 01:38:16.500
Yes. sir?

1360
01:38:17.250 --> 01:38:20.250
You faxed a photo of a person
and requested his details.

1361
01:38:20.500 --> 01:38:21.976
Yes. sir.
We sent it across all stations.

1362
01:38:22.000 --> 01:38:23.917
Why did you ask for his details?

1363
01:38:30.625 --> 01:38:31.625
How do you know him. sir?

1364
01:38:31.792 --> 01:38:32.958
Eight years ago.

1365
01:38:33.042 --> 01:38:36.333
I was put in a special team
to nab a criminal named Abraham.

1366
01:38:36.583 --> 01:38:37.583
<i>Unfortunately.</i>

1367
01:38:37.708 --> 01:38:40.583
I had to leave the team
after an accident.

1368
01:38:41.000 --> 01:38:44.583
If that accident hadn't happened
and I'd stayed with the team.

1369
01:38:44.833 --> 01:38:47.167
I wouldn't be talking to you today.

1370
01:38:50.125 --> 01:38:51.875
<i>He's the most wanted
underground criminal.</i>

1371
01:38:53.000 --> 01:38:55.542
<i>He comes out
only for important assignments.</i>

1372
01:38:56.583 --> 01:38:59.667
No one knows where he is at other times.

1373
01:39:00.208 --> 01:39:03.083
He operates alone without a team.

1374
01:39:03.292 --> 01:39:05.375
We found it difficult to trace him

1375
01:39:05.500 --> 01:39:08.583
because hardly anyone had seen him.

1376
01:39:08.833 --> 01:39:09.833
except for a select few.

1377
01:39:09.958 --> 01:39:11.542
<i>His name is all that anyone knows.</i>

1378
01:39:20.958 --> 01:39:22.199
Call me if anything goes wrong.

1379
01:39:24.792 --> 01:39:26.512
- Pass me the car key.
- Where are you off to?

1380
01:39:26.875 --> 01:39:29.750
That 100-rupee note must get here
before Varun's manager arrives.

1381
01:39:30.667 --> 01:39:33.083
See what you can do to find out
about your brother.

1382
01:39:34.042 --> 01:39:36.000
I'll do my best from my side.

1383
01:39:41.458 --> 01:39:42.500
Don't go alone.

1384
01:39:43.167 --> 01:39:44.250
Take my guys with you.

1385
01:39:45.125 --> 01:39:46.125
No need.

1386
01:39:46.500 --> 01:39:47.583
I'll take care of it.

1387
01:39:57.958 --> 01:40:00.875
<i>Because he was involved in several
high-profile murders.</i>

1388
01:40:01.292 --> 01:40:05.042
<i>senior officials immediately ordered
an operation to take him down.</i>

1389
01:40:05.667 --> 01:40:07.625
<i>So. at that time.</i>

1390
01:40:08.083 --> 01:40:11.083
they selected the state's top 15
encounter specialist officers

1391
01:40:11.458 --> 01:40:13.167
for the mission.

1392
01:40:13.708 --> 01:40:14.792
<i>A tip revealed</i>

1393
01:40:15.167 --> 01:40:19.208
that he was planning to kill
a prominent businessman at a luxury hotel.

1394
01:40:19.792 --> 01:40:22.500
The team decided to confront him there.

1395
01:40:23.375 --> 01:40:25.792
A total of 16 people died
in the operation.

1396
01:40:29.708 --> 01:40:32.625
Fifteen of them were people
who had gone there to kill him.

1397
01:40:38.917 --> 01:40:40.792
The last one was the man he came to kill.

1398
01:40:41.375 --> 01:40:42.375
Please don't!

1399
01:40:45.792 --> 01:40:46.875
After that incident.

1400
01:40:47.042 --> 01:40:50.750
everyone feared for their lives
and avoided the case.

1401
01:40:51.167 --> 01:40:53.417
Since then. he has remained inactive
for several years.

1402
01:41:08.542 --> 01:41:10.750
No information about him
surfaced after that.

1403
01:41:16.750 --> 01:41:17.958
Now that he's back.

1404
01:41:18.833 --> 01:41:20.167
something big is about to happen.

1405
01:41:24.917 --> 01:41:26.083
<i>Because of our mistake.</i>

1406
01:41:26.292 --> 01:41:29.625
<i>innocent lives are paying the price.</i>

1407
01:41:31.875 --> 01:41:34.042
We need to act to prevent this.

1408
01:41:35.500 --> 01:41:37.417
We must first find out where they are.

1409
01:41:37.958 --> 01:41:39.292
How do we find that out. Dad?

1410
01:41:41.292 --> 01:41:44.917
The guy who learned karate
and is now a cop…

1411
01:41:45.083 --> 01:41:46.083
What's his name?

1412
01:41:46.458 --> 01:41:47.458
Gautham. Dad.

1413
01:41:51.417 --> 01:41:53.750
Gautham. I need to tell you something.

1414
01:41:54.042 --> 01:41:55.042
Go ahead. Master.

1415
01:41:56.875 --> 01:41:58.125
I'll tell you in person.

1416
01:42:06.458 --> 01:42:07.458
Udhaya…

1417
01:42:09.917 --> 01:42:11.797
- Sir.
- Have the people at the scene reported in?

1418
01:42:12.208 --> 01:42:16.042
They're checking near the bridge.
but there's no evidence yet.

1419
01:42:20.375 --> 01:42:22.458
Where is Muthukumar?
I don't see him around.

1420
01:42:22.542 --> 01:42:24.583
He got a call that his father was sick.

1421
01:42:24.833 --> 01:42:26.042
so he went home.

1422
01:42:33.875 --> 01:42:35.250
Trust me.

1423
01:42:36.000 --> 01:42:37.500
His brother isn't with us.

1424
01:42:37.792 --> 01:42:38.833
So. Toby…

1425
01:42:40.125 --> 01:42:41.833
Really didn't tell you anything?

1426
01:42:42.417 --> 01:42:43.417
No.

1427
01:42:45.292 --> 01:42:47.125
He didn't tell us anything.

1428
01:42:49.375 --> 01:42:52.375
That karate master's daughter
withdrew the case.

1429
01:42:52.625 --> 01:42:53.625
You mean…

1430
01:42:59.833 --> 01:43:00.833
What did you say?

1431
01:43:05.167 --> 01:43:07.250
- The karate master's daughter?
- Yes.

1432
01:43:08.167 --> 01:43:10.292
That's why Toby couldn't do
anything to her.

1433
01:43:13.375 --> 01:43:15.250
I swear. I'm telling the truth.

1434
01:43:16.250 --> 01:43:17.542
He's not with us.

1435
01:43:18.167 --> 01:43:19.208
Trust me.

1436
01:43:21.833 --> 01:43:22.875
I believe you.

1437
01:43:26.708 --> 01:43:28.167
You're telling the truth.

1438
01:44:11.417 --> 01:44:12.417
Wait. I'll go.

1439
01:44:20.375 --> 01:44:21.375
Who are you?

1440
01:44:22.083 --> 01:44:23.083
What do you want?

1441
01:44:44.875 --> 01:44:47.116
What did you do to those
six people who came to kill you?

1442
01:44:51.208 --> 01:44:52.583
He's part of their group. Mom.

1443
01:44:53.375 --> 01:44:56.000
He'd know where
the inspector's wife and son are.

1444
01:45:12.625 --> 01:45:15.417
<i>In the joint attack by America and Israel.</i>

1445
01:45:15.500 --> 01:45:18.625
<i>Iran's Supreme Leader.
Ali Khamenei. was killed.</i>

1446
01:45:18.708 --> 01:45:21.542
<i>as confirmed by news sources.</i>

1447
01:46:45.083 --> 01:46:46.750
- Yeah. tell me?
<i>- Rajaram.</i>

1448
01:46:46.833 --> 01:46:49.667
<i>why's your TV so loud?
Turn the volume down.</i>

1449
01:48:29.417 --> 01:48:30.417
Dear…

1450
01:50:54.833 --> 01:50:56.417
Sir. I've pulled up a list of places

1451
01:50:56.500 --> 01:50:59.708
that will profit us in the long run
in the Keelakadu project.

1452
01:50:59.958 --> 01:51:02.083
If we invest in
and operate our mining sites.

1453
01:51:02.167 --> 01:51:05.833
we'll become India's leading
mineral supplier within ten years.

1454
01:51:08.333 --> 01:51:09.333
That sounds good!

1455
01:51:09.500 --> 01:51:10.833
Buddy. stop!

1456
01:51:11.458 --> 01:51:13.292
- What?
- We can get booze here.

1457
01:51:13.375 --> 01:51:14.750
- Over here?
- Yeah!

1458
01:51:15.292 --> 01:51:16.167
Dude!

1459
01:51:16.250 --> 01:51:17.250
Hey!

1460
01:51:20.417 --> 01:51:23.750
<i>The number you're trying
to call is currently not reachable.</i>

1461
01:51:28.042 --> 01:51:29.042
Hey!

1462
01:51:29.500 --> 01:51:31.250
Where is the inspector's family?

1463
01:51:31.833 --> 01:51:32.833
Tell me.

1464
01:51:33.083 --> 01:51:34.667
Answer me.

1465
01:51:35.000 --> 01:51:36.000
Answer me!

1466
01:51:39.292 --> 01:51:40.417
- Yeah. tell me.
- Bro.

1467
01:51:40.750 --> 01:51:42.375
I feel something's off.

1468
01:51:50.750 --> 01:51:54.917
- What's the matter?
- I just met with my informant.

1469
01:51:55.417 --> 01:51:58.375
Her dad's a karate master.
not a headmaster.

1470
01:51:58.833 --> 01:52:02.333
- Where are you going with this?
- His daughter is like him. it seems.

1471
01:52:02.708 --> 01:52:07.375
I was wondering if
they did something to our men.

1472
01:52:07.833 --> 01:52:09.792
I hope not. but.

1473
01:52:10.208 --> 01:52:11.833
I know they're not to be messed with.

1474
01:52:26.083 --> 01:52:28.000
So. my brother…

1475
01:54:10.042 --> 01:54:11.917
Check where the officer's family is.

1476
01:54:26.083 --> 01:54:28.458
They're inside. all tied up. Dad.

1477
01:54:32.875 --> 01:54:34.167
Looks like we don't need him.

1478
01:54:34.375 --> 01:54:38.250
You think it's game over
once you kill me and rescue them?

1479
01:54:39.458 --> 01:54:40.458
Of course.

1480
01:54:57.833 --> 01:55:00.208
Sir. everyone's here.
Should we start?

1481
01:55:03.625 --> 01:55:05.500
Yes. let's party!

1482
01:55:08.750 --> 01:55:09.750
Who's he?

1483
01:55:10.125 --> 01:55:13.167
I told you it isn't game over yet.

1484
01:55:13.917 --> 01:55:15.597
There's another guy.
more powerful than us.

1485
01:55:15.708 --> 01:55:16.708
He works for him.

1486
01:55:17.042 --> 01:55:19.208
You have something that interests him.

1487
01:55:19.708 --> 01:55:23.042
And he'll hunt you down until he gets it.

1488
01:55:24.042 --> 01:55:25.042
What is that. exactly?

1489
01:55:31.708 --> 01:55:33.125
All this over a 100-rupee note?

1490
01:55:33.458 --> 01:55:34.833
I'm not falling for this crap.

1491
01:55:35.292 --> 01:55:36.625
Don't believe me. fine.

1492
01:55:37.000 --> 01:55:38.281
Ask him. and he'll say the same.

1493
01:55:39.042 --> 01:55:40.042
Hey!

1494
01:55:41.708 --> 01:55:44.125
What's so special about that note?

1495
01:55:44.875 --> 01:55:46.625
<i>But this Black Opal
is far more valuable.</i>

1496
01:55:46.917 --> 01:55:48.684
Its current market worth
is more than 70 billion.

1497
01:55:48.708 --> 01:55:50.750
When we drill below 1.500 feet…

1498
01:55:51.000 --> 01:55:54.750
Transfer ten billion
into my trust as legitimate funds.

1499
01:55:58.042 --> 01:56:00.667
We'll get that amount
only if we give the 100-rupee note.

1500
01:56:04.958 --> 01:56:08.333
Ask your uncle to verify his statement.

1501
01:56:23.417 --> 01:56:24.417
Uncle?

1502
01:56:24.958 --> 01:56:26.875
Yes. dear.
As you said. there's a purse.

1503
01:56:27.125 --> 01:56:28.125
We took it out.

1504
01:56:28.667 --> 01:56:30.067
and there's a 100-rupee note in it.

1505
01:56:35.583 --> 01:56:36.875
Dad. the note's in there.

1506
01:56:37.917 --> 01:56:40.625
More than anything else.
my life is important to me.

1507
01:56:41.375 --> 01:56:44.792
If I'm going to stay alive.
that 100-rupee note has to reach him.

1508
01:56:45.417 --> 01:56:47.250
So just give me the note.

1509
01:56:48.042 --> 01:56:49.083
and this all ends here.

1510
01:56:50.917 --> 01:56:52.917
But if you kill me before that.

1511
01:56:53.500 --> 01:56:55.708
he will hunt you down for it.

1512
01:56:56.208 --> 01:56:57.708
He'll destroy your family.

1513
01:57:04.875 --> 01:57:06.042
Remember that.

1514
01:57:23.250 --> 01:57:26.125
Our family. our peace…
It's all gone to ruin!

1515
01:57:30.833 --> 01:57:32.792
He will hunt you down for it.

1516
01:57:33.083 --> 01:57:34.542
<i>He'll destroy your family.</i>

1517
01:57:44.875 --> 01:57:45.958
- Nila…
- Yes?

1518
01:57:51.833 --> 01:57:55.583
I feel we'll be in trouble
if we don't give him that note.

1519
01:57:57.625 --> 01:57:58.625
What do we do?

1520
01:58:00.417 --> 01:58:01.417
You tell me.

1521
01:58:03.625 --> 01:58:06.042
Just hand over the note.
That's it.

1522
01:58:25.708 --> 01:58:31.167
So the villagers' lives
mean nothing to you?

1523
01:58:31.250 --> 01:58:32.583
You're overthinking it now.

1524
01:58:32.917 --> 01:58:35.500
Why do you care?
They have nothing to do with you.

1525
01:58:36.167 --> 01:58:39.458
Don't lose your life
trying to save theirs.

1526
01:58:39.833 --> 01:58:42.000
Well. you're right.

1527
01:58:43.375 --> 01:58:45.833
They have nothing to do with us.

1528
01:58:47.250 --> 01:58:49.333
But there's something you must know.

1529
01:58:50.917 --> 01:58:52.917
Remember those two we tried to save?

1530
01:58:54.458 --> 01:58:56.333
You think we knew them beforehand?

1531
01:58:58.000 --> 01:59:00.917
If we can put in so much effort
to save their lives.

1532
01:59:01.750 --> 01:59:02.750
then think…

1533
01:59:23.792 --> 01:59:28.667
<i>We planted our lives in this soil
And laid our loved ones to rest here.</i>

1534
01:59:28.750 --> 01:59:33.667
<i>Every leaf and every vine
Belongs to us like blood and kin.</i>

1535
01:59:34.333 --> 01:59:39.125
<i>Here we found our lives
And here we lost our people too.</i>

1536
01:59:39.208 --> 01:59:44.500
<i>These hills and these lands
Are the Gods we pray to.</i>

1537
01:59:44.792 --> 01:59:49.667
<i>The greatness of this land runs deep.</i>

1538
01:59:50.000 --> 01:59:55.167
<i>And we live by its will.</i>

1539
01:59:55.250 --> 02:00:00.083
<i>This land is the God we worship.</i>

1540
02:00:00.375 --> 02:00:05.167
<i>And this wind is the mother
That holds us close.</i>

1541
02:00:14.958 --> 02:00:17.583
Don't do it!
Hey. make him stop!

1542
02:00:18.875 --> 02:00:20.333
My daughter's made up her mind.

1543
02:00:21.333 --> 02:00:23.042
Once it's done. it's done.

1544
02:00:26.792 --> 02:00:27.792
Goodbye!

1545
02:00:49.708 --> 02:00:50.708
<i>Hello. Control Room.</i>

1546
02:00:57.917 --> 02:00:58.917
It's okay.

1547
02:00:59.000 --> 02:01:00.958
We're fine. We're okay.
Everything's fine.

1548
02:01:01.458 --> 02:01:02.708
Poor Harish…

1549
02:01:08.833 --> 02:01:11.917
<i>Reports indicate that
one of the nine deceased</i>

1550
02:01:12.125 --> 02:01:15.500
<i>is Ravikanthan. the manager of prominent
businessman Varun Dayalan.</i>

1551
02:01:15.917 --> 02:01:19.792
<i>This development has sent shock waves
through the business community.</i>

1552
02:01:20.292 --> 02:01:22.042
<i>Forensics experts and…</i>

1553
02:01:22.125 --> 02:01:26.708
Release a statement saying he has been
away for a week due to personal reasons.

1554
02:01:28.333 --> 02:01:33.000
<i>The bodies have been sent to the
government hospital for postmortem.</i>

1555
02:01:33.250 --> 02:01:35.417
<i>The motives behind the murder…</i>

1556
02:01:35.583 --> 02:01:38.542
You said it was coming.
but there's nothing.

1557
02:01:38.875 --> 02:01:41.792
<i>Funny how your name
shows up everywhere.</i>

1558
02:01:42.167 --> 02:01:44.375
What's really going on?

1559
02:01:44.625 --> 02:01:45.958
There's been a minor issue.

1560
02:01:47.125 --> 02:01:49.250
<i>The money I sent
is held up somewhere.</i>

1561
02:01:49.458 --> 02:01:51.542
I've sent my men to check on it.

1562
02:01:52.083 --> 02:01:53.667
Give me some time.

1563
02:01:53.875 --> 02:01:57.417
I'll make sure it reaches you
safe and sound.

1564
02:01:57.792 --> 02:02:02.375
Why do I feel like you're trying
to rope me into trouble?

1565
02:02:03.167 --> 02:02:05.458
I'll ensure nothing troubles you.

1566
02:02:05.958 --> 02:02:08.292
<i>A day's time is all I need.</i>

1567
02:02:08.667 --> 02:02:11.375
- I'll fix this mess.
- Alright. you got it.

1568
02:02:11.917 --> 02:02:13.317
<i>And if it doesn't reach me by then.</i>

1569
02:02:13.792 --> 02:02:17.250
I'll have to call off the deal
we discussed.

1570
02:02:28.083 --> 02:02:29.667
- Purushothaman?
- Yes. sir?

1571
02:02:30.292 --> 02:02:32.125
Got anything?
Something?

1572
02:02:32.333 --> 02:02:34.667
Not yet. sir.
Our men are still on the lookout.

1573
02:02:36.500 --> 02:02:40.000
The sooner we get it. the better.

1574
02:02:40.750 --> 02:02:44.583
- Keep me posted every 15 minutes.
- Yes. sir.

1575
02:02:44.667 --> 02:02:47.101
It must be the same gang
that kidnapped Kirubakaran's brother.

1576
02:02:47.125 --> 02:02:49.208
Find out if Kirubakaran
had issues with anyone.

1577
02:02:49.500 --> 02:02:52.708
especially people
who might've wanted him dead.

1578
02:02:52.875 --> 02:02:57.167
Review all the CCTV footage
covering the incident area.

1579
02:02:57.417 --> 02:03:00.333
Investigate every person
who passed by that place.

1580
02:03:00.417 --> 02:03:01.750
- Okay?
- Yes. sir!

1581
02:03:02.917 --> 02:03:05.625
I need to review your CCTV footage
for a case.

1582
02:03:05.750 --> 02:03:07.958
But your officers already
came in the morning for it.

1583
02:03:08.042 --> 02:03:09.708
- Our officers?
- Yes. sir.

1584
02:03:09.792 --> 02:03:11.083
I'm not lying.

1585
02:03:11.167 --> 02:03:13.000
Their IDs looked real.
so we gave it to them.

1586
02:03:14.792 --> 02:03:17.875
Hey. did you send our men out
on rounds this morning?

1587
02:03:17.958 --> 02:03:19.250
No. sir. I didn't.

1588
02:03:22.000 --> 02:03:23.875
It wasn't our men who got the footage.

1589
02:03:25.750 --> 02:03:26.750
But someone else.

1590
02:03:47.792 --> 02:03:51.250
Here's the CCTV footage
from around the place. sir.

1591
02:03:52.917 --> 02:03:55.667
This is the only way
you can enter that street.

1592
02:03:55.792 --> 02:03:57.667
And they should've taken
this way out.

1593
02:04:03.125 --> 02:04:05.208
Sir. a group of men showed fake IDs

1594
02:04:05.292 --> 02:04:08.167
and got CCTV footage
from the surrounding area.

1595
02:04:08.708 --> 02:04:12.458
This seems like the killer's attempt
to cover their tracks.

1596
02:04:13.333 --> 02:04:15.042
Got the reports. sir.

1597
02:04:15.125 --> 02:04:17.833
No one else's fingerprints were present
except the deceased's.

1598
02:04:39.750 --> 02:04:40.750
It's you.

1599
02:04:43.667 --> 02:04:46.250
- What's up?
- Boss asked you to settle the bill.

1600
02:04:46.833 --> 02:04:47.833
It isn't settled yet?

1601
02:04:51.792 --> 02:04:53.792
It's nothing.
My uncle is right here praying.

1602
02:04:54.208 --> 02:04:56.375
Anyway. forget that.
Today at the office…

1603
02:05:05.250 --> 02:05:09.125
We've killed and buried six people
in the last eight hours.

1604
02:05:10.333 --> 02:05:13.750
I'm going crazy thinking about…

1605
02:05:15.875 --> 02:05:17.125
What's going to happen next.

1606
02:05:22.333 --> 02:05:25.500
I'm scared for my family.

1607
02:05:43.083 --> 02:05:45.875
What do we have to do

1608
02:05:46.792 --> 02:05:48.167
to be at peace and end it all?

1609
02:05:48.417 --> 02:05:50.167
Sir. very few people live there.

1610
02:05:50.333 --> 02:05:51.917
In the three hours before the incident.

1611
02:05:52.000 --> 02:05:54.833
only two scooters
and four motorcycles passed by.

1612
02:06:05.292 --> 02:06:06.375
We have one more to kill…

1613
02:06:07.667 --> 02:06:08.958
To end this game.

1614
02:06:14.000 --> 02:06:15.042
We can't do anything…

1615
02:06:16.417 --> 02:06:17.458
Until he's dead.

1616
02:06:24.500 --> 02:06:26.875
You think you can escape
that easily?

1617
02:06:27.458 --> 02:06:28.500
We'll be caught like mice.

1618
02:06:28.958 --> 02:06:32.167
Things will worsen
if we do nothing about it.

1619
02:06:33.208 --> 02:06:34.958
We have no ties to him.

1620
02:06:35.792 --> 02:06:38.875
No one would even suspect
that we killed him.

1621
02:06:40.375 --> 02:06:41.375
Only catch?

1622
02:06:42.375 --> 02:06:43.750
We must do it…

1623
02:06:44.708 --> 02:06:46.083
While covering our tracks.

1624
02:07:12.458 --> 02:07:13.458
I thought it through.

1625
02:07:14.042 --> 02:07:15.083
and you're right.

1626
02:07:15.583 --> 02:07:16.667
Let's end him.

1627
02:07:19.125 --> 02:07:20.625
What do we do with him. though?

1628
02:07:33.417 --> 02:07:34.708
It can't be them.

1629
02:07:35.167 --> 02:07:37.333
Bring everyone in except those two.

1630
02:08:24.458 --> 02:08:25.542
It wasn't me.

1631
02:08:26.333 --> 02:08:28.375
But I saw who did it.

1632
02:08:37.750 --> 02:08:38.958
You did?

1633
02:08:39.250 --> 02:08:40.250
Yes. sir.

1634
02:08:41.833 --> 02:08:45.958
The police are already after me
for an illicit liquor case.

1635
02:08:46.458 --> 02:08:50.083
I thought I'd hide somewhere
no one would come.

1636
02:08:50.250 --> 02:08:51.250
So I went there.

1637
02:08:51.625 --> 02:08:54.333
That's when I heard
a strange noise

1638
02:08:54.708 --> 02:08:56.583
<i>from a building nearby.</i>

1639
02:09:03.458 --> 02:09:05.792
Will you recognize them?

1640
02:09:39.792 --> 02:09:41.208
Sir. sir. sir…

1641
02:09:50.083 --> 02:09:51.083
Yes. boss.

1642
02:09:51.417 --> 02:09:52.777
Send in everyone you can round up.

1643
02:09:53.833 --> 02:09:55.000
<i>You have one hour.</i>

1644
02:09:55.583 --> 02:09:57.042
<i>I want that 100-rupee note.</i>

1645
02:10:02.292 --> 02:10:03.750
NEELAVENI RESIDENCE

1646
02:10:16.208 --> 02:10:18.542
Sir. the accountant's here to see you.

1647
02:10:18.625 --> 02:10:19.625
Let him through.

1648
02:11:22.708 --> 02:11:25.250
We'll be in trouble if any of them dies.

1649
02:11:26.500 --> 02:11:27.583
So. don't kill anyone.

1650
02:11:27.917 --> 02:11:30.917
No one is leaving here alive.

1651
02:14:49.167 --> 02:14:50.167
Who are you?

1652
02:14:52.292 --> 02:14:53.875
What did I ever do to you?!

1653
02:14:54.542 --> 02:14:57.083
We'll get that amount
only if we give the 100-rupee note.

1654
02:14:57.917 --> 02:14:59.833
Just hand over the note.

1655
02:15:00.583 --> 02:15:01.583
What do we do?

1656
02:15:06.208 --> 02:15:07.208
Tell us. dear.

1657
02:15:09.875 --> 02:15:11.125
Let's…

1658
02:15:11.833 --> 02:15:12.833
Burn that note.

1659
02:15:17.833 --> 02:15:18.833
<i>This is what we'll do.</i>

1660
02:15:25.417 --> 02:15:29.083
You don't have to know the victim
to stand up for them.

1661
02:15:29.458 --> 02:15:31.125
<i>Every injustice must be confronted!</i>

1662
02:15:31.542 --> 02:15:34.125
<i>That's when our lives gain meaning.</i>

1663
02:15:47.917 --> 02:15:49.125
Die. you sewer rat!

1664
02:16:03.750 --> 02:16:07.542
Sir. I reviewed the CCTV footage
we recovered.

1665
02:16:07.917 --> 02:16:12.750
Varun's men got to it before ours did.

1666
02:16:13.125 --> 02:16:15.458
And I strongly believe
he's somehow connected to this.

1667
02:16:15.542 --> 02:16:16.542
What?

1668
02:16:17.292 --> 02:16:18.542
- Varun?
- Yes. sir.

1669
02:16:18.625 --> 02:16:21.458
Kirubakaran must have
killed Varun's manager.

1670
02:16:21.667 --> 02:16:24.542
So. Varun may have taken revenge
by killing Kirubakaran.

1671
02:16:24.625 --> 02:16:28.125
He must have removed the
CCTV footage to destroy the evidence.

1672
02:16:30.083 --> 02:16:33.167
We'll only get answers
once we take him into custody.

1673
02:16:33.250 --> 02:16:34.250
Yes. sir.

1674
02:16:39.167 --> 02:16:40.167
Hello?

1675
02:16:52.417 --> 02:16:53.417
What did you say?

1676
02:16:53.792 --> 02:16:54.792
Varun's dead?!

1677
02:17:11.000 --> 02:17:12.083
<i>Here's the latest.</i>

1678
02:17:12.167 --> 02:17:13.708
<i>Three months later.</i>

1679
02:17:13.875 --> 02:17:18.875
<i>the murders of Varun Dayalan
and his men remain unsolved.</i>

1680
02:17:18.958 --> 02:17:22.500
<i>continuing to shock the public.</i>

1681
02:17:22.792 --> 02:17:27.667
<i>Police investigations
into his business rivals</i>

1682
02:17:27.792 --> 02:17:31.875
<i>have produced no useful leads.</i>

1683
02:17:32.167 --> 02:17:37.500
<i>There are reports that the case
is being transferred to the CBI…</i>

1684
02:17:38.305 --> 02:18:38.249
Do you want subtitles for any video?
-=[ ai.OpenSubtitles.com ]=-
